  {title: "Iron Man (1968) #297", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 297, marvel_id: 9546, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/60/5a749ffe41669/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1998) #34", modified: "2014-01-23T11:05:34-0500", issue_number: 34, marvel_id: 17517, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/e0/585c2b3033d16/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Count Nefaria threatens to turn the world's population into his own demented puppets with the power of an ionic energy bomb!"},
  {title: "All-New Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 1: Communication Breakdown (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-11-15T14:35:57-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 62149, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/60/5a0ca902d0e4c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "A new era of cosmic adventure begins! The Guardians of the Galaxy have taken off into space once more on their biggest and weirdest misadventures yet! Kicking things off with the boldest heist they've ever pulled, Star-Lord, Rocket and company blast their way through the galaxy - with the peacekeepers of the Nova Corps hot on their tail! And soon enough, they find themselves caught in a war between the Collector and the Grandmaster! Will there be any room to explain why Groot can't grow any bigger, what Gamora is searching for, or why Drax has sworn off violence?! You bet there will - the all-new Guardians of the Galaxy has space for all your Marvel Cosmic needs! Collecting Free Comic Book Day 2017 All-New Guardians of the Galaxy #1, All-New Guardians of the Galaxy (2017) #1-2, 4, 6, 8, 10."},
  {title: "All-New Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2: Riders in the Sky (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-12-13T18:58:49-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 62150, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/f0/5a31941285e1a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Collects All-New Guardians of the Galaxy #3, 5, 7, 9, 11-12. Catch up with your favorite Guardians as they share the galactic spotlight! Gamora - the most dangerous person in the galaxy - is hiding something. What is her secret quest? Star-Lord sails the galaxy's radio waves, keeping up with the one piece of home he could never leave behind! Discover the reason behind Drax the former Destroyer's vow of peace! Learn what happened to Groot that caused him to revert to a tiny shrub - and why Rocket thinks it's all his fault! Plus: Meet the members of the resurgent Nova Corps as they come into desperate conflict with the shadowy Fraternity of Raptors! And as the Guardians return to Earth in the aftermath of SECRET EMPIRE, who will join them as their newest member?"},
  {title: "All-New X-Men (2012) #24 (Keown Variant)", modified: "2014-03-03T11:44:17-0500", issue_number: 24, marvel_id: 49943, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/e0/5314b082e7bea/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "<ul><li>X-Men and Guardians vs. Gladiator and Jean Grey&#39;s fate lies in the balance!</li><li>One of the X-Men&#39;s lives will be forever changed!</li></ul>"},
  {title: "Annihilation Classic (Hardcover)", modified: "2017-12-08T16:17:59-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 22433, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/00/4bb6c85261aaf/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Space may be a vacuum, but Annihilation didn't pull its heroes out of nowhere! Journey through time, space and continuity with the sensational space saga's stars! The re-making of Adam Warlock and the first look at his nemesis Thanos! See the origin of Nova and the origin of Quasar, while Bug watches the origins of >tik< EVERYBODY! Monsters, mammals and more! Collecting BUG #1, TALES TO ASTONISH #13, NOVA #1, QUASAR #1, ROCKET RACCOON #1-4, MARVEL SPOTLIGHT #6, LOGAN'S RUN #6 and MARVEL PREMIERE #1.\r<br>Rated A...$29.99 \r<br>ISBN: 978-0-7851-3388-9\r<br>Trim size: oversized\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #4", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:21-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 20686, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/b0/4e83879785c16/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The cosmic blockbuster thunders on - with our villains on the verge of victory! Ultron gets his hands on Star-Lord! Ronan makes a chilling revelation! Adam Warlock gets the shock he never expected! Writers Dan Abnett and Andy Lanning join forces with superstar artist Tom Raney to bring you the sci-fi event that Wizard calls \"Mystery, action and adventure on a galactic scale!\"\r<br>Rated T+  ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #5", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:22-0500", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 20885, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/90/4e8389572567c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Can anyone stop Ultron? How did the evil android unite with the Phalanx? What are his secret plans? And have any of our desperate and divided heroes survived to fight back? It's not too late to join the acclaimed team of writers Dan Abnett & Andy Lanning (NOVA) and penciler Tom Raney (ULTIMATE X-MEN) for another chapter of what Wizard raves is \"mystery, action and adventure on a galactic scale!\"\r<br>Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #6", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:22-0500", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 21016, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/50/4e81eebde62e0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "This is it: Marvel's rag-tag group of sci-fi heroes vs. Ultron - in a double-sized finale! The surviving warriors face-off on the battlefield, with the fate of the entire Kree Empire - and perhaps the Earth itself - at stake! Who will fall? Who will rise to become a legend? It's an extra helping of adventure, humor, drama and eye-candy that IGN.com calls \"one of the best event books of the year.\"\r<br>Rated T+ ...$3.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest - Starlord (2007) #3", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:19-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 16598, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/80/51df288b4fbaf/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "On a no-win, no-tech suicide mission, Starlord and his rag-tag band of cosmic cult favorites struggle to recover from a huge loss, but they have no time to rest and reflect as their vicious foes unleash hell!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest - Starlord (2007) #4", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:20-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 16599, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/80/51df29e9e311d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Will Peter Quill and his ragtag squad succeed in their adventure - or is it truly a suicide mission? Hordes of the Phalanx close in on Starlord, Bug, Captain Universe, Deathcry, Groot, Mantis and Rocket Raccoon-and one may make the supreme sacrifice!"},
  {title: "The Mighty Captain Marvel (2017) #128", modified: "2018-01-24T16:13:17-0500", issue_number: 128, marvel_id: 65902, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/d0/5a68ec5cdd8bf/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "DARK ORIGIN PART 4. DANVERS VS. QUILL! The Prize—the REALITY STONE! But will the power of this unearthed artifact be enough to pull Carol back to reality, or is this merely the first step in a much larger quest?"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2013) #1", modified: "2016-06-28T15:31:19-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 43305, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/60/573deeae53730/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "There's a new rule in the galaxy: No one touches Earth! No one!! Why has Earth become the most important planet in the Galaxy? That's what the Guardians of the Galaxy are going to find out!! Join the brightest stars in the Marvel universe: Star Lord, Gamora, Drax, Rocket Raccoon, Groot and--wait for it--Iron-Man, as they embark upon one of the most explosive and eye-opening chapters of Marvel NOW! These galactic Avengers are going to discover secrets that will rattle Marvel readers for years to come! Why wait for the movie? It all starts here!"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2008) #20", modified: "2015-01-23T11:14:45-0500", issue_number: 20, marvel_id: 25308, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/10/517ad68878d23/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "REALM OF KINGS. The Guardians have been to hell and back to save the universe itself. But after their monumental efforts, could it be that - due to the creation of The Fault-the universe is an even more dangerous place than before?"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #197", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 197, marvel_id: 7060, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/90/58861814775ff/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Annihilation (2006) #5", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:46-0400", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 5655, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/c0/51b61262eac63/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "With the war lost, Ronan and the very, very angry Super-Skrull kill their way to the heart of the Kree Empire. VIVE LA KREE!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #1", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:21-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 17271, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/30/4e8381b35e231/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "This is it, the beginning of the next Annihilation main event! In the PROLOGUE, the Phalanx launched a sneak attack on the Kree Empire, in NOVA, QUASAR, STAR-LORD and WRAITH, heroes separated by distance but united by willpower took their first steps to liberating a galaxy in peril. Now all the threads begin to weave together -- and if you thought the surprises were over, think again! What are the Phalanx really after? What new players will change the game? And what last-page reveal will leave your jaw hanging? Grab your weapon and join the fight for freedom with the powerhouse creative team of writers Dan Abnett & Andy Lanning and penciler Tom Raney (ULTIMATE X-MEN)! \r<br>Rated A ...$2.99"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #2", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:21-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 17405, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/50/4e8384c84cd95/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The sci-fi event of the year continues here! The Big Bad behind the entire saga was revealed on the last page of last issue - but what does this fan-fave villain want? And what does it have to do with the surprise ally that our heroes have also recently found? Plus: Who survived the STAR-LORD series to fight on here? And what about the motley crew led by Ronan? The titanic team of Andy Lanning & Dan Abnett (NOVA) and Tom Raney (ULTIMATE X-MEN) deliver the answers fast and furious in this issue!\r<br>Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest (2007) #3", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:21-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 17645, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/00/4e83867ba1c87/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The cosmic blockbuster rocks on-as things go horribly wrong for our heroes! The Phalanx closes in on Star-Lord and his scrappy squad, Ronan comes face-to-face with a vengeful enemy, and Quasar & Moondragon discover a deep secret that could save the Kree...but they both might be dead before they can use it! Writers Dan Abnett and Andy Lanning join forces with superstar artist Tom Raney to bring you the sci-fi event that Aint It Cool News says is \"...a worthy sequel and every bit the equal to the impressively cohesive and thoroughly entertaining crossover event ANNIHILATION from last year!\"\r<br>Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Super-Skrull (2006) #1", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4110, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/c0/578791d73a15a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Super-Skrull bursts into the frontline of the war against the Annihilation Wave-taking the fight to the enemy in his own ruthless way. And for once, evil may just be the only way to defeat evil!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Super-Skrull (2006) #2", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 4220, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/c0/5787988337a8a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Pitted against an enemy superweapon, Super-Skrull's quest takes him behind enemy lines, where an evil scientist and a planet of alien scum may be his only hope for victory!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Super-Skrull (2006) #3", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 4317, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/10/51df2f988a27e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Super-Skrull has built an army of villains united under a common goal: to frag the Annihilation Wave all the way back to the Negative Zone, but as the final battle draws close, a betrayal in the ranks may spell doom for Super-Skrull and his crusade!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Super-Skrull (2006) #4", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 4472, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/80/5787a44424450/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Super-Skrull's crusade against the Annihilation Wave has ended in failure, but the eradication of everything he sought to preserve has only made Super-Skrull a greater threat! The Super-Skrull strikes back!"},
  {title: "Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #14", modified: "2014-08-05T14:09:26-0400", issue_number: 14, marvel_id: 21366, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/60/58dbce634ea70/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The fates of The Initiative, the United States, and Planet Earth hang in the balance. Plus: Former Avenger, Delroy Garret, assumes the mantle and arsenal of Earth's greatest Skrull-Hunter, The 3-D Man."},
  {title: "Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #14 (SPOTLIGHT VARIANT)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 14, marvel_id: 24571, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/30/4e948fb5e9b52/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Irredeemable Ant-Man (2006) #1", modified: "2015-06-25T17:26:26-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 5199, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/70/58498477421c8/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Introducing the world's worst superhero! When a S.H.I.E.L.D. agent gets a hold of Hank Pym's new Ant-Man suit, you know there's trouble. He's not concerned with saving the world. He's concerned with getting through the day and getting a leg up on life!"},
  {title: "Irredeemable Ant-Man Vol. 1: Low-Life (2007)", modified: "2016-12-08T11:27:39-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 15894, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/70/4bc353d839901/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Introducing the world's worst super hero! When a low-level S.H.I.E.L.D. agent gets a hold of Hank Pym's new Ant-Man suit, you know the Marvel Universe is in trouble. He's not concerned with saving the world or helping others. He's concerned with getting through the day and getting a leg up on life. He's not going to use his powers responsibly, he's going to use them for the betterment of himself. He's Ant-Man, a new \"hero\" for the modern world. If you thought Robert Kirkman pushed the boundaries of what could be in a Marvel Comic with MARVEL ZOMBIES just wait until you see what he does in here! \r<br>Collecting IRREDEEMABLE ANT-MAN #1-6.\r<br>144 PGS./Rated T+ ...$9.99\r<br>ISBN: 0-7851-1962-0\r<br>"},
  {title: "Namor: The Sub-Mariner (1990) #17", modified: "2018-01-19T11:40:11-0500", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 66021, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/10/5a6227cc0e239/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Super-Skrull has taken Namor hostage!"},
  {title: "Namor: The Sub-Mariner (1990) #18", modified: "2018-01-19T11:41:16-0500", issue_number: 18, marvel_id: 66022, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/50/5a612f879b1b2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "A battle against the Iron Fist-impersonating Super-Skrull in the Savage Land!"},
  {title: "Nova (2007) #16", modified: "2014-08-05T14:09:28-0400", issue_number: 16, marvel_id: 21739, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/90/578fae0b41d85/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SECRET INVASION TIE-IN Is our always-outnumbered space cop actually teaming with one of the enemy? Featuring Super-Skrull!"},
  {title: "GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY: AWESOME MIX INFINITE COMIC (2016) #9", modified: "2017-01-20T11:52:32-0500", issue_number: 9, marvel_id: 62678, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/a0/58823f7009f1b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Part Two. Someone claiming to be the legendary Star-Lord has got the real Star-Lord in a heap of trouble!"},
  {title: "GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY: AWESOME MIX INFINITE COMIC (2016) #10", modified: "2017-01-31T17:26:01-0500", issue_number: 10, marvel_id: 62683, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/20/58910ec868174/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Peter Quill and Groot had an adventure! But what exactly happened?"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #198", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 198, marvel_id: 7061, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/a0/5886190d1e0a9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "THOR EPIC COLLECTION: THE WRATH OF ODIN TPB (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-09-20T17:28:30-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 60486, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/30/59c2e2164788f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "A masterpiece of immortal action and boundless drama, Stan Lee and Jack Kirby's Thor is a cornerstone of the Marvel Universe. And in this Epic Collection, Thor's saga explodes onto the cosmic stage with the debut of Ego the Living Planet! And the action continues nonstop with the High Evolutionary, Ulik the Troll and the unstoppable Destroyer! Then, Loki conspires to have Odin strip Thor of his power and banish him to Earth. Stranded, Thor must struggle to survive the machinations of his scheming half-brother, while attempting to return to All-Father Odin's good graces! Plus the return of Lady Sif, and battles against the Growing Man, Replicus, the Super-Skrull...and your favorite enchanted-crowbar-wielding galoot, the Wrecker! Collects Thor (1966) #131-153, Annual (1966) #2."},
  {title: "Legendary Star-Lord (2014) #1", modified: "2016-07-11T17:12:49-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 50887, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/40/53a889daadda2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "From the pages of GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY!\nA brand new series from SAM HUMPHRIES and PACO MEDINA! In this exciting first issue, Peter Quill battles the Badoon, fights to save an orphanage, and still finds time for some flirting with Kitty Pryde--but it's all in a day's work for the STAR-LORD!"},
  {title: "Marvel Premiere (1972) #61", modified: "2016-11-23T13:40:26-0500", issue_number: 61, marvel_id: 10252, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/03/57f5132b93892/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The final issue of Marvel Premiere! Present a truly bizarre science-fiction blockbuster starring everyone’s favorite intergalactic troublemaker: Star-Lord."},
  {title: "Marvel Preview (1977) #4", modified: "2016-11-23T13:43:49-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 19776, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/50/57f54e958058a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "This is where it all begins! Get ready for the cosmic origin of Star-Lord! (note: this contains the Star-Lord story only)"},
  {title: "All-New Guardians of the Galaxy (2017) #7", modified: "2017-07-28T16:44:13-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 61519, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/03/596d07e521810/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Drax has long been known as \"The Destroyer\" - but no more! He has forsaken all violence, and sworn never to again strike another in anger! And now, guest artist Greg Smallwood joins series writer Gerry Duggan to reveal what led our boy down the road of peace!"},
  {title: "All-New Wolverine (2015) #23", modified: "2017-08-04T16:50:13-0400", issue_number: 23, marvel_id: 60513, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/60/5977943607f2d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "WOLVERINE VERSUS BROOD - SO MANY BROOD! With hundreds of BROOD coming at them and no end in sight, is this the final chapter in WOLVERINE's story? Will the combined might of the GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY be any help at all? Will we see a FASTBALL SPECIAL involving DRAX and Wolverine? I sure hope so!"},
  {title: "Annihilation (2006) #1", modified: "2017-11-21T12:24:39-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4788, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/d0/51b61283075b2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "One empire has fallen. Two heroes are dead.It all comes together here! Individually, the Silver Surfer, Super-Skrull, Ronan and Nova have faced down the Annihilation Wave... and lost! Now, they must unite those who remain or die by Annihilus' hand!  The Annihilation has only begun!"},
  {title: "Annihilation (2006) #3", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:46-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 5230, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/00/51b612534e2e6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Nova's United Front is divided. Nova sets off on a desperate mission. Ronan heads to Hala to free the Kree race. And everyone else is just trying to survive! And what's Drax's secret agenda, anyway?"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Nova (2006) #2", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:44-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 4221, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/c0/578557a046083/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "To protect the legacy of the Xandarian culture, Nova must escape from the burning ruins of the homeworld. But can he trust himself to use his new power wisely, or will he lose control again and pose a  threat to the cosmos greater than the invasion itself? And on the subject of trust, how far can he trust his new 'friend'... Drax? \r<br>32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Nova (2006) #4", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 4473, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/d0/578646de5027a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Driven to regain his dignity and burdened by the fate of Xandar, Nova faces the Annihilation Wave head on and unleashes the full power of the Nova Force! But is that enough against such a vast force of cosmic destruction? And if it isn't, who will stand with him in that last battle? Quasar? Drax?\r<br>Guest starring QUASAR and DRAX THE DESTROYER!\r<br>Interlocking cover with all three other ANNIHILATION covers! \r<br>32 PGS./Rated A ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #219", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 219, marvel_id: 7085, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/50/587fc9fa8e181/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #220", modified: "2015-11-02T13:47:10-0500", issue_number: 220, marvel_id: 7087, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/a0/5873c01012bde/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers Annual (1967) #16", modified: "2017-10-19T17:17:31-0400", issue_number: 16, marvel_id: 6930, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/5a294cc49f30b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Captain Marvel (1968) #43", modified: "2018-01-11T13:52:16-0500", issue_number: 43, marvel_id: 8032, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/80/5a58f6bcbd328/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Supreme Intelligence brings Captain Marvel and Drax the Destroyer out to a desolate moon to confront one another!"},
  {title: "Captain Marvel (1968) #44", modified: "2018-01-11T13:54:39-0500", issue_number: 44, marvel_id: 8033, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/50/5a58f5aedf015/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Fawn alerts Mar-Vell of Rick Jones' condition, and the Captain rushes to the rescue!"},
  {title: "Drax (2015) #7", modified: "2016-05-13T14:16:32-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 56871, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/e0/5734d2d3813a0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Drax’s adventures in babysitting continue! To get worse! It’s bad enough Drax has to take these tots to monster-infested, poisoned-aired planets (we assume)—what if he starts CARING about them?!? Your blood will BOIL with the thrill of battle! Your heart will be WARMED by unlikely friendships!"},
  {title: "Drax (2015) #8", modified: "2016-06-17T15:06:53-0400", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 56872, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/00/57640819dd159/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Drax’s mission to return all of the Fin Fang Foom refugee children continues to go well. Except, you know, for all the bounty hunters after him. Ironically, one of the bounty hunters is CAMMI, another child Drax was tricked into caring about. Will she lead him to the person who put the hit out on Drax? Who are those other bounty hunters she’s with? Oh, only PIP THE TROLL and…PLANET TERRY???"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Ronan (2006) #2", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 4219, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/d0/578660897592d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Godthab Omega: a nothing planet in a backwater bit of the cosmos. Right? Wrong. In fact, something is very wrong on Godthab, a malign presence drawing in cosmic entities like flies to a web. Ronan's been snagged too, and he's not happy about it. In fact, he's going to do something about it... right after he deals with the \"deadliest woman in the Universe,\" Gamora! And, as if that impending confrontation weren't enough to shake Godthab to its core, here comes the Annihilation Wave...\r<br>32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Ronan (2006) #3", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 4316, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/e0/578665baac782/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MYSTERY MASTERMIND REVEALED!\r<br>Cosmic powerhouses Ronan and Gamora get it on... big time: a truly planet-shattering conflict that will, quite literally, reshape an entire world. Don't miss this important issue that helps redefine the cosmic map as we know it! This tragic series can only end with... Annihilation!\r<br>32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #72", modified: "2013-08-09T17:37:17-0400", issue_number: 72, marvel_id: 7324, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/f0/586e594ce0813/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The She-Hulk is gone, and Jennifer Walters is on the run! Her friends aren't sure what she's afraid of, but they'll find out!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Ronan (2006) #4", modified: "2014-09-18T14:51:45-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 4471, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/c0/57866a57dd22b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The dreams of a mad god die screaming as the Annihilation Wave descends on the recreated Godthab Omega. And in the middle of it all, Ronan, torn between saving as many lives as possible and a quickly disappearing chance to clear his name. Ultimately, the price of Ronan's newfound freedom... may well be his life! Guest starring GAMORA!\r<br>Interlocking cover with all three other ANNIHILATION covers! \r<br>32 PGS./Rated A ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Gamora (2016) #1", modified: "2016-12-12T12:22:14-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 51841, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/50/584b0e8aecf3b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Before the Guardians…there was Gamora! From screenwriter Nicole Perlman—co-writer of the Guardians of the Galaxy screenplay—and Marvel superstar artist Marco Checchetto comes a killer new ongoing series! Once upon a time she was Thanos’ heartless pet assassin and favorite daughter. Today, she is the backbone of the Guardians of the Galaxy, putting her life on the line to defend the innocent. What was it that transformed her from being used as a tool of her oppressor, to a champion of the powerless? Embark on a journey of revenge and redemption, and witness how Gamora earned her reputation as the Deadliest Woman in the Galaxy."},
  {title: "Gamora (2016) #2", modified: "2017-01-13T10:32:32-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 51843, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/50/5873fda85529e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "OUT OF TIME AND OUT FOR REVENGE! The story continues as we follow GAMORA to the doomed planet that is UBLIEX. Perched on the brink of a black hole, its inhabitants count down the hours to their planet’s imminent demise as it is swallowed up by the approaching Singularity. Will Gamora find her revenge among the inhabitants of Ubliex before the black hole consumes them all? Or will the citizens of this world — including a doomsday cult, junkie bounty hunters and a young woman with a tremendous destiny — stop her first?"},
  {title: "Gamora (2016) #3", modified: "2017-02-10T11:43:03-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 51845, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/b0/589deaf0cb6e4/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "ON THE DOOMED PLANET UBLIEX, ESCAPE IS IMPOSSIBLE! While the planet literally breaks apart around her, GAMORA searches for her prey, determined to get her revenge against the BADOON – even if it’s the last thing she does! But on Ubliex, where adventure and criminals wait around every corner, Gamora might find more than she ever imagined…a truth so astounding that it will rock Gamora to her very core."},
  {title: "Gamora (2016) #4", modified: "2017-03-16T09:17:14-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 51846, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/40/58cac3ad39d25/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SUNRISE ON DOOMSDAY! As planet Ubliex approaches the black hole’s event horizon, GAMORA is on the cusp of getting the revenge she so desperately seeks…in exchange for making deals with gangsters of questionable intent, who claim they hold the key to escape. Yet as earthquakes, fire tornadoes and anti-gravity bubbles begin to tear Ubliex to pieces, Gamora may find herself forced to choose between her vengeance quest and her own survival."},
  {title: "Gamora (2016) #5", modified: "2017-05-26T10:15:12-0400", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 51847, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/80/5925b4656c40d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "DOOMSDAY ON UBLIEX! As the black hole begins to tear UBLIEX apart at the seams, GAMORA has her eyes on the only thing that can save her: the last remaining piece of the Elemental Crystal. If she can steal it back from L’Wit, then hijack and jumpstart a spaceship before the city is destroyed, she may just have a chance to survive. But time is running out, and L’WIT, KLAXON and the VESTIGIALS are all standing in her way... The clock is ticking, so Gamora better hit the ground running…"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2013) #1 (Manara Variant)", modified: "2013-03-11T16:18:06-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 46138, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/b0/513e3b03e473a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "There&rsquo;s a new rule in the galaxy: No one touches Earth! No one!! Why has Earth become the most important planet in the Galaxy? That&rsquo;s what the Guardians of the Galaxy are going to find out!! Join the brightest stars in the Marvel universe: Star Lord, Gamora, Drax, Rocket Raccoon, Groot and--wait for it--Iron-Man, as they embark upon one of the most explosive and eye-opening chapters of Marvel NOW! These galactic Avengers are going to discover secrets that will rattle Marvel readers for years to come! Why wait for the movie? It all starts here!"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2013) #2", modified: "2015-06-08T14:00:07-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 43304, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/50/573e047e0770b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "<ul><li>While London deals with the brutal Badoon invasion, the fate of the Guardians of the Galaxy may have been decided millions of miles away.</li></ul>"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2015) #9", modified: "2016-06-02T12:38:11-0400", issue_number: 9, marvel_id: 55472, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/03/5750603b7566d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "GAMORA AND DRAX FIGHT A MONSTER OF THE BADOON! The two most deadly people in the galaxy together again! Drax and Gamora go on a side mission involving the Badoon that’s going to put their skills to the test like never before. But the Badoon aren’t just playing the same old game and these Guardians are going to have to learn the rules really quickly."},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2015) #12", modified: "2016-09-16T12:18:24-0400", issue_number: 12, marvel_id: 55475, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/60/57d2c401492e7/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Guardians’ allegiances are split right down the middle, and tensions have NEVER been higher! Will they be too busy fighting to guard the galaxy? Will that even matter if they can’t leave Earth?"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2008) #17", modified: "2017-05-05T11:05:51-0400", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 25305, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/10/517ad6a215852/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "WAR OF KINGS TIE-IN In order to save the universe, Adam Warlock takes desperate action and seeks the help of allies you won't believe!"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy (2015) #17", modified: "2017-02-03T09:33:13-0500", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 60979, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/03/58823356c509a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Angela has come a long way from the skies of Heven…to find herself grounded on the Earth. Can she find a new home among the heroes?"},
  {title: "Guardians of the Galaxy: Dream On (2017) #1", modified: "2017-10-20T14:07:12-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 61146, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/f0/58f1075430250/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE GUARDIANS ARE DONE GUARDING THE GALAXY, YES? When one of the galaxy’s greatest bounty hunters targets the Guardians of the Galaxy, it’s lights out for STAR-LORD, GAMORA, DRAX, ROCKET and GROOT! But if DEATH’S HEAD can make their dreams come true, will the Guardians fight back, or go along with his crazy plan? They might…especially if it leads to the destruction of THANOS once and for all! Also included - a special presentation of GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY (1990) #1, featuring the first appearance of Taserface!"},
  {title: "Astonishing X-Men (2004) #27", modified: "2014-05-01T15:16:02-0400", issue_number: 27, marvel_id: 21941, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/04/58f7bad86fcf5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "GHOST BOX PART 3 Upon study of the Ghost Box technology left behind at the Subject X murder scene, the X-Men uncover a conflict between artificially created mutants and mutants from another reality!"},
  {title: "Annihilation: Conquest - Starlord (2007) #2", modified: "2015-12-15T16:04:19-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 16191, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/90/51df26f6f3ec3/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Briefed, outfitted and dropped into chaos, it's time for Bug, Captain Universe, Deathcry, Groot, Mantis and Rocket Raccoon to become legends! That is, if Peter Quill can truly embrace his legacy as Starlord!"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #1", modified: "2014-08-08T10:50:59-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 36644, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/d0/5784f71eaa933/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Marvel U's most powerful heroes come together for the fight of their lives! When the Dire Wraiths strike, the Annihilators assemble the heaviest hitters in the entire universe to save the day!"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #2", modified: "2014-08-29T12:21:14-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 36647, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/40/5785004a15618/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Spaceknights and the Dire Wraiths have returned! As the Wraith's deadly foul magic returns, the home world of the Spaceknights looks as if it will be the first to fall. Only the Annihilators stand between the Wraiths and galactic conquest!"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #2 (DAVIS VARIANT)", modified: "2011-04-04T09:00:14-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 38640, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/c0/4d35abb1088b3/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "They're back: The Spaceknights and the Dire Wraiths! As the Wraith's deadly Black Sun ascends and their foul magicks return, the home world of the SpaceKnights looks as if it will be the first planet to fall to their might! Only the awesome Annihilators, the newest and most powerful Marvel team of all, stand between the Wraiths and total galactic conquest! Meanwhile, Rocket Raccoon races to Planet X to rescue his old buddy Groot. But what is the secret from Rocket's past that is coming back to haunt him? All this, plus a variant cover by B.P.R.D.'s Guy Davis!"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #3", modified: "2014-07-30T16:26:19-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 36646, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/50/578501593d399/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "As the battle rages on between the Annihilators and the Dire Wraiths, it seems as if the Dire Wraiths may be too strong for even the Annihilators to handle. What will the conclusion to this epic battle mean for the rest of the Marvel Universe?"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #3 (DJURDJEVIC VARIANT)", modified: "2011-04-29T09:38:28-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 38641, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/03/4d51664595b04/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The most powerful super team ever-that's right, we said it-faces the threat of the infamous Dire Wraiths! But can a squad that includes Silver Surfer, Gladiator and Beta-Ray Bill defeat this diabolical race and the dark magic they are unleashing?  Meanwhile, Rocket Raccoon and Groot zoom deeper into their adventure as Rocket's secret and slightly crazy origin is revealed!"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #4", modified: "2012-04-19T15:18:12-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 36645, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/b0/57850169f2432/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Annihilators finally reach the epic conclusion of their battle with the Dire Wraiths. Will the Annihilators manage to prove that they have what it takes to be the protectors of the universe, or will they fall to the Dire Wraiths' magic?"},
  {title: "Annihilators (2010) #4 (VARIANT)", modified: "2011-06-02T16:46:36-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 38643, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/03/4d88b33007528/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "TWO AWESOME STORIES IN ONE COSMIC BOOK! This is it: the galaxy's most powerful squad and most beloved duo face their fiery finales! First, the Annihilators must prove they are the ace team of universal protectors that Star-Lord dreamed they could be...or perish in the attempt! Meanwhile, Rocket Raccoon and Groot face the horrible, reality-twisting menace - who has a key connection to Rocket's secret past - that lurks in the heart of the Half-World Asylum! Want to show the House of Ideas that you want more Marvel Cosmic? Spread the word and buy this issue!"},
  {title: "Annihilators: Earthfall (2011) #1", modified: "2011-09-26T15:46:57-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 39982, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/30/578533577248b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MARVEL'S COSMIC HEAVY HITTERS COME TO EARTH-AND FIGHT THE AVENGERS! What has brought Gladiator, Quasar, Ronan, Ikon and Beta-Ray Bill to our planet...and why are they at odds with Earth's Mightiest Heroes? All this, plus each issue will feature a five-page chapter of an all-new, all-hilarious Rocket Raccoon & Groot story!"},
  {title: "Annihilators: Earthfall (2011) #2", modified: "2011-10-26T16:12:00-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 39981, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/60/5785390cbe1c2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE GALAXY'S MOST MAGNIFICENT!From the fallout of ANNIHILATION and the end of the GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY, an all-too-familiar cosmic threat has returned, this time with Earth as his beachhead. His followers span a thousand worlds, awaiting only the word to begin new wars in his name... unless the ANNIHILATORS can silence him first! So why do THE AVENGERS stand in their way, and what are the true stakes if either side fails? Plus, continuing our backup adventure, it's MOJO versus ROCKET RACCOON & GROOT onstage for a high-stakes campy cosmic free-for-all!"},
  {title: "Annihilators: Earthfall (2011) #3", modified: "2011-11-17T13:14:31-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 39980, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/80/56b8be1651644/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "From the pages of The Thanos Imperative, the evil prophet of the Universal Church of Truth has been reborn! The Magus once sacrificed dozens of worlds to the dark gods of the Cancerverse. Now the Magus has deified himself, with Earth as his pulpit, and mankind as his enslaved congregation! Can the Annihilators and the Avengers work together to stop him, when the Annihilators are prepared to destroy the Earth to save the galaxy?"},
  {title: "Deadpool: Too Soon? Infinite Comic (2016) #3", modified: "2016-11-29T13:13:32-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 57901, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/80/57976f9136d53/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SOMEONE HAS MURDERED FORBUSH MAN! Could someone be targeting all of Marvel’s funniest characters for death? That’s what Deadpool thinks, and now he’s gotta act before someone bumps off SQUIRREL GIRL, ROCKET RACCOON, GROOT, ANT-MAN, HOWARD THE DUCK and THE PUNISHER! (Like we said, the funny characters.) Good thing Deadpool is renowned for his investigative skills!"},
  {title: "Deadpool: Too Soon? Infinite Comic (2016) #8", modified: "2016-10-14T16:32:01-0400", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 57906, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/50/58013f90652be/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The magnificent murder mystery comes to an end! Who’s been killing all of Deadpool’s friends and what is Wade going to do about it? Your answers lie here!"},
  {title: "Guardians of Infinity (2015) #7", modified: "2016-06-03T12:48:39-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 59481, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/00/5751b462958c6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "God of the Newcomers HERMETIKUS was there at the inception of the GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY…\nand if he has his way, he’ll be there at the END! And writer ROBBIE THOMPSON (VENOM: SPACE KNIGHT, SILK, SPIDEY) reveals more about the noble, mysterious SPACE KNIGHTS!"},
  {title: "Astonishing X-Men (2004) #28", modified: "2014-05-01T15:16:09-0400", issue_number: 28, marvel_id: 23087, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/70/58f7c091de4a1/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "GHOST BOX PART 4 Upon arriving in Tian, China, the X-Men encounter a team of hostile mutants, mutants who have a connection to one of their own: former X-Man Forge!"},
  {title: "I Am Groot (2017) #1", modified: "2017-05-19T11:35:34-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 62828, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/60/591c9bb7abe25/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "GROOT IN HIS OWN SERIES, SMALLER AND BETTER THAN EVER! When the Guardians of the Galaxy get caught in a wormhole, a smaller-than-normal Groot is separated billions of light-years away from the team. Falling to a planet below, Groot discovers he is on an entirely alien and unknown world full of strange creatures and societies. Seriously underdeveloped and with nobody who can understand him, Groot will need to make the journey to the center of this world and find the way back to his family!"},
  {title: "I Am Groot (2017) #2", modified: "2017-06-23T12:58:29-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 63241, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/70/594c2aac7b9b6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Trapped on a world that doesn't understand him!! Groot is stuck on a strange alien planet, but the first step in finding a way home is for someone who can translate \"I am Groot.\" This isn't gonna be easy…"},
  {title: "I Am Groot (2017) #3", modified: "2017-07-21T15:22:44-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 63867, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/a0/596d12482be4e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Groot and his new friends go off on a quest to get home! But will Groot realize there's a traitor in his midst? And how will he react when he meets some very familiar-looking strangers?"},
  {title: "A YEAR OF MARVELS: SEPTEMBER INFINITE COMIC (2016) #1", modified: "2016-09-09T14:28:47-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 57931, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/00/57c99a120a3ea/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "In September, TIPPY-TOE is flying SOLO (until Squirrel Girl is done studying)! But when a villain threatens Central Park, she’s gotta call in the big guns. Enormous guns, relatively speaking (because Tippy and ROCKET RACCOON are small)! It’s the team-up — written by Nilah Magruder — you would have demanded if you knew your worth! You’re wonderful, and you deserve beautiful things!"},
  {title: "Deadpool: Too Soon? (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-03-17T14:48:36-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 60165, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/c0/58cc3af443d87/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "When Forbush Man is murdered, could it be the beginning of a killing spree that's no laughing matter? Deadpool sure thinks so! Things are about to get serious for Marvel's funniest characters as the Merc with a Mouth sets about saving hilarious heroes including Squirrel Girl, Rocket Raccoon, Groot, Ant-Man, Howard the Duck and…Punisher?! If that plot ain't nuts enough, brace yourself for Squirrelpool! As the bodies start to pile up, Wade and Howard investigate why their pals keep losing their heads — literally! Maybe Doctor Strange, Master of the Mirthful Arts, can work his magic and help put an end to this killing joke before Deadpool becomes the punchline! It's a Marvel Universe murder mystery that'll have you in tears — of laughter, or sorrow, or possibly both! Collects Deadpool: Too Soon? #1-4 & Gwenpool Holiday Special: Merry Mix-Up 1 (Deadpool story)."},
  {title: "1602 (2003) #7", modified: "2013-07-30T10:52:58-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 145, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/90/568e6b71aabd8/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Secrets are revealed and coffins are closed as two of our 17th-century Marvel heroes lose their lives in the penultimate chapter to this major, best-selling limited series event!\r\n32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$3.50"},
  {title: "Age of X: Alpha (2010) #1", modified: "2017-03-21T11:32:48-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 37996, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/10/59762093434e7/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Mutantkind's final war starts here. If you don't know which side you're on, check  your DNA."},
  {title: "Age of X: Alpha (2010) #1 (Variant)", modified: "2017-07-24T14:25:33-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 37973, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/40/image_not_available/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Mutantkind's final war starts here. If you don't know which side you're on, check your DNA."},
  {title: "All-New X-Men (2012) #1", modified: "2015-07-16T17:32:12-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 43462, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/d0/584b119c32e98/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Marvel Now! The five original X-Men have been plucked from yesteryear and sent to the present. How will they deal with the current state of Xavier's dream, and how will today's X-Men cope with facing their former selves?"},
  {title: "All-New X-Men (2012) #4", modified: "2014-08-05T14:08:51-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 43469, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/70/584b161418efc/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "- The Original 5 X-Men come face to face with their counterparts...and it isn't a peaceful meeting!"},
  {title: "Alpha Flight (1983) #17", modified: "2017-06-06T15:16:52-0400", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 12676, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/80/5939a478bdc79/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Heather Hudson becomes the new leader of Alpha Flight!"},
  {title: "Alpha Flight (1983) #33", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 33, marvel_id: 12694, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/40/image_not_available/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1963) #327", modified: "2012-03-27T15:22:10-0400", issue_number: 327, marvel_id: 6735, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/e0/57c74ebfbb94e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man: Renew Your Vows (2016) #7", modified: "2017-05-05T11:32:36-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 61356, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/e0/5908be7835f30/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Magneto strikes! The Brotherhood of Evil Mutants has defeated the X-Men…and now it’s up to the Spider-Family to stop them!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man: Renew Your Vows Vol. 2 - The Venom Experiment (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-11-22T12:34:59-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 62102, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/e0/5a15c2156b66b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The sensational adventures of the spectacular Spider-Family continue! And this time they’re joined by…the X-Men! Annie Parker just received an invitation to attend Xavier’s School for Gifted Youngsters — which means she’ll get to meet Wolverine, Cyclops, Jean Grey and Professor X! But where the X-Men go, can Magneto and his Brotherhood of Evil Mutants be far behind? Then, Mary Jane has been saving the day as Spinneret, but at the cost of some of her husband’s powers — so it’s time for a biological upgrade. Something black and white and terrible all over. Face it, Tiger — MJ is Venom! But will she give in to the symbiote’s villainous urges? Speaking of which, say hello to 10-year-old Norman Osborn II! Can he escape the Goblin family legacy? Collecting THE AMAZING SPIDER-MAN: RENEW YOUR VOWS (2016) #6-12."},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #47", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 47, marvel_id: 7296, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/c0/5865398d33f69/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #48", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 48, marvel_id: 7297, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/10/586544734ea93/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #49", modified: "2015-04-28T11:52:14-0400", issue_number: 49, marvel_id: 7298, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/c0/58654d16baf65/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #53", modified: "2011-12-08T15:19:45-0500", issue_number: 53, marvel_id: 7303, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/d0/5866720842525/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
