  {title: "Agents of Atlas (2009) #3 (Wolverine Art Appreciation Variant)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 24017, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/20/4bb4e5e8d1801/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Back in the 1950's our heroes fall deeper into the mystery of the Dragon's Corridor- leading them to Communist plots and two mysteriously familiar bodies on ice. In the present day, a similar trail of intrigue winds back to secret plans of the Atlas Foundation. The Agents look to be building a hellish arsenal for Norman Osborn, and they've just gotten the attention of none other than CAPTAIN AMERICA!\r\nParental Advisory ...$2.99"},
