  {title: "All-New X-Men (2012) #2", modified: "2014-05-15T17:54:37-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 43467, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/50/584b138ada8af/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Professor X's five original students have been flung from the past to present day. While they cope with an unimaginable future (especially considering the fallout of AVX), how will today's X-Men justify their actions to their past selves?"},
