  {title: "Astonishing X-Men (2004) #66", modified: "2013-09-04T10:57:09-0400", issue_number: 66, marvel_id: 45827, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/60/58f8fe20a7ac1/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "- In the aftermath of Iceman's assault on the world, the X-Men need some time to breathe and reflect, and take stock of their relationships.\n- What will come from this?\n- And will it send one character down a new path away from the X-Men?"},
  {title: "Astonishing X-Men (2004) #67", modified: "2013-09-06T16:27:20-0400", issue_number: 67, marvel_id: 45828, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/b0/58f8ff5cbb10f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "- Wolverine and Gambit - on the road - in a stolen Lamborghini...\n...With an alien stuffed in the teeny tiny trunk - and more aliens tailing them.\n- What could possibly go wrong?"},
  {title: "Clandestine Classic Premiere (Hardcover)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 20731, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/90/4bc31676581d6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "For centuries they have lived among us - mysterious, elusive, unknowable...so what are they doing with brightly colored costumes and codenames?! Teenagers Rory and Pandora want to pull Alan Davis's family of extra-normal outsiders into the world of heroes and villains, little knowing that M.O.D.O.K. and A.I.M. are waiting for them! Centuries-old patriarch Adam Destine knows the disastrous duo has a lot to learn about power and responsibility...and we all know who's the web-spinning specialist on that, don't we? Plus Adam and his super-powered scions join the X-Men in a demonic debacle against the sinister Synraith! Also guest-starring Doctor Strange, the Silver Surfer and the Invaders! Collecting CLANDESTINE #1-8, MARVEL COMICS PRESENTS #158 and X-MEN & CLANDESTINE #1-2.\r<br>Rated T+ ...$29.99 \r<br>ISBN: 978-0-7851-2742-0\r<br>"},
  {title: "All-New X-Men (2012) #6", modified: "2014-05-15T17:54:37-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 43471, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/70/584b17f6424d1/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The future of the X-Men will be defined by their past!  How are the teenage X-Men going to fix their future?"},
  {title: "Decimation: Generation M (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2016-09-27T12:48:58-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 4275, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/80/4bc5e2b9784ac/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "House of M has changed the world forever. Now, from the ashes of this cataclysmic event comes a new generation...GENERATION M. Find out exactly HOW things have changed as a group of mutants brought together by this common tragedy must fight together for a better tomorrow. Collects GENERATION M #1-5.\r<br>120 PGS./Rated T+ ...$13.99\r<br>ISBN: 0-7851-1958-2\r<br>"},
  {title: "Generation M (2005) #2", modified: "2016-09-27T12:31:56-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 3209, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/e0/57ea9ec081ff5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "DECIMATION! Reporter Sally Floyd tells the story of those rocked by the decimating effects of House of M.  One such story is that of Frederick J. Dukes, A.K.A. The Blob!  There's someone out there that doesn't want these stories to be told and is willing to do anything to silence those who are talking...\r<br>32 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #1", modified: "2017-05-12T13:00:31-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 62820, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/c0/59121ed9d4f72/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Xavier Institute for Mutant Education and Outreach has opened its doors and is ready to foster the next generation of heroes and diplomats! But this time around, the X-Men recognize an unfortunate truth: not all mutants are created equal. Some mutants are not made to fight Sentinels or serve as ambassadors on behalf of their kind. Some mutants will just be lucky to survive another day in a world that hates and fears them. And who better to mentor mutantkind’s lovable losers than perpetual sidekick Jubilee? But will Jubilee and GENERATION X survive the experience??"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #2", modified: "2017-05-26T10:20:26-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 62821, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/03/5925b4348611e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Xavier Institute is put on lockdown when mutant-hunting PURIFIERS infiltrate the campus! And even though Jubilee’s charges are ordered out of harm’s way, some of her students can’t help but enter the line of fire. Class has only been in session for one day, and GENERATION X is about to learn some important lessons the hard way…"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #3", modified: "2017-06-09T14:49:43-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 62932, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/60/593992c881ebe/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Something is lurking in the shadows of Central Park…a monster that steals mutants in the night. And when GENERATION X takes it upon themselves to investigate…they might just find themselves face-to-face with an all too familiar threat."},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #4", modified: "2017-07-07T16:30:46-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 63702, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/00/595ea9fc33194/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Taking it upon themselves to catch the assailant who's been attacking mutants in Central Park, the Xavier Institute's \"Lovable Losers\" go on the hunt for the culprit. But they aren't prepared when the trail leads them right to Generation X's most formidable foe…EMPLATE returns! Only she isn't the same monster they once knew…"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #5", modified: "2017-08-11T14:00:24-0400", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 64209, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/50/597bbb9bba9aa/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "All eyes on EYE-BOY! The most diligent student at the Xavier School for Mutant Education and Outreach is about to learn the most difficult lesson of all: When you can see EVERYTHING, you end up seeing some things you wish you hadn't!"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #6", modified: "2017-08-25T12:53:55-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 64382, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/c0/599afcdddd4d2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "With a mutant-killing monster loose beneath New York City, the X-Men impose a curfew for the students of the Xavier Institute. But QUENTIN QUIRE's never much been one to follow rules..."},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #7", modified: "2017-10-13T18:01:11-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 64907, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/59dfda500a547/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Morph, Kid Omega, and Hindsight are trapped!! Stuck in a villain-infested auction, the Gen Xers must destroy a priceless weapon all without getting caught by the auctioneer, Kade Kilgore. No big whup, right?"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #8", modified: "2017-11-01T15:01:15-0400", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 65072, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/e0/59fa124559de5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Spotlight on Monet! When we last found Monet St. Croix, she had merged with her vampiric brother, Emplate. Now, cursed with the hunger to feast on others…she has set her sights on Jubilee’s new class!"},
  {title: "Generation X (2017) #86", modified: "2018-01-10T14:56:48-0500", issue_number: 86, marvel_id: 65907, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/40/5a56688e3069e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Survival of the Fittest PART 2. The kids of Generation X are trapped inside the X-Mansion with M-Plate stalking them! Now, without Jubilee, Gen X must defend themselves from the vampire mutant. All this, plus…the return of another original Gen X-er! Who is it? You gotta read to find out!"},
  {title: "Generation X Vol. 1: Natural Selection (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-10-27T15:25:30-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 65124, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/80/59f38ea070722/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Xavier Institute for Mutant Education and Outreach has opened its doors, and is ready to foster the next generation of heroes and diplomats! But this time around, the X-Men recognize an unfortunate truth: not all mutants are created equal. Some mutants are just not made to fight Sentinels or serve as ambassadors on behalf of their kind. Some mutants will be lucky just to survive another day in a world that hates and fears them. These are the students who should be kept out of harm's way when the Purifiers target the campus! And who better to mentor mutantkind's lovable losers through life out of the limelight...than perpetual sidekick Jubilee! But will her Generation X survive the experience?! Collecting Generation X (2017) #1-6."},
  {title: "Jubilee (2004) #1", modified: "2017-05-16T16:09:22-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 789, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/a0/591b5c624c29f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "X-MEN: RELOAD ANOTHER CLIP!  \r<br>Join Jubilee, everyone's favorite wisecracking mutant firecracker, in her new adventures on the left coast! Living in the X-Mansion was a trip, but now she's found where \"mutants\" really come out-her old stomping grounds of Lo"},
  {title: "Jubilee (2004) #2", modified: "2017-05-16T16:11:05-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 861, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/d0/591b5cc459d9a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Get ready for fast times at Payton-Noble High School! Jubilee's come back to California, and the local prep squad had better watch out! She's got explosive mutant powers and an attitude to match, but when her new best friend and P.N.H.S.'s #1 nerd, Meg De"},
  {title: "Jubilee (2004) #3", modified: "2017-05-16T16:10:50-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 50, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/30/591b5cb4e699f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Payton-Noble High's newest and spunkiest recruit, Jubilee, finds herself caught between her classmates and an L.A. gang rivalry. Can everyone's favorite mutant mallrat handle it in the barrio, or will Jubilee fall prey to South Central's own special blend of hospitality? And what the heck is Aunt Hope doing with all those firearms?"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #203", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 203, marvel_id: 7068, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/40/587fa755268af/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "5 Ronin (2010) #4 (MACK COVER)", modified: "2011-03-22T01:31:02-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 38752, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/80/4d8105b95b48c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "5 Books, 5 Heroes-1 unforgettable story of heroes pushed to their limits.  It is 17th century Japan, a time and place of violent upheaval, wandering Ronin, and mysterious Geisha. Into this strange and dangerous world come Wolverine, Pyslocke, Punisher, Hulk and Deadpool. Five of Marvel's greatest heroes...as you've never seen them before. Each has been wronged by a powerful tyrant. Each has taken a solemn vow...of vengeance!\n5 Books, 5 Heroes, 5 Weeks...1 spell-binding story."},
  {title: "Avengers Assemble Vol. 4 (Hardcover)", modified: "2017-12-06T10:59:47-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 5844, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/10/585c2f83a501a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Avengers embark on international adventure against a nation-sized knight and a city of Hulks! Then, it's off to small-town Centerville to face Salem's Seven and the Sons of the Serpent! Plus: A major Marvel crossover! Avengers in space, and inquiries answered by the man who knows Earth's Mightiest Heroes best! Collecting AVENGERS #35-40 and ANNUAL 2000-2001, AVENGERS: THE ULTRON IMPERATIVE, and MAXIMUM SECURITY #1-3 and DANGEROUS PLANET.\r<br>416 PGS./Rated T+ ...$34.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Avengers Vs. X-Men: Versus (2011) #4", modified: "2013-04-02T15:33:37-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 42489, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/90/4fe876943fc92/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The battle between the Avengers and the X-Men rages on. With Hope's life itself in the balance, Emma goes head to head with Iron Man! It's mentalist vs. metal man!"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #16", modified: "2017-06-21T16:39:44-0400", issue_number: 16, marvel_id: 7389, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/20/594c3c1065cbe/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The X-Men vs. the Phalanx! Along with Cyclops, Jean Grey, and Wolverine, Cable stages an all-out assault on the Phalanx citadel! Can they take it down, or is all of mutantkind doomed to assimilation?"},
  {title: "Doctor Strange, Sorcerer Supreme (1988) #46", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 46, marvel_id: 20208, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/40/image_not_available/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
