  {title: "Uncanny X-Force (2010) #26", modified: "2014-02-19T10:27:22-0500", issue_number: 26, marvel_id: 40443, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/10/594286dacaf9f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "X-FORCE is put to the test when a powered group named the OMEGAS battle some of the team's strongest members! Meanwhile, Psylocke goes to the Jean Grey School for Higher Learning to visit an old friend, but what she finds may shock her to the core!"},
