  {title: "All-Winners Squad: Band of Heroes (2011) #3", modified: "2011-08-05T16:17:36-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 29735, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/50/56b21f4988287/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Discover the shocking truth behind the World War II adventures of Marvel's original heroes, as Captain America, Bucky, and the valiant men of the military's all-superhuman squadron give all to defeat the Axis! But a sinister secret lies behind their mission...and it takes no less a meddler than Loki, the God of Trickery, to bring it to light!"},
