  {title: "Deadpool: World's Greatest Vol. 9 - Deadpool in Space (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-09-06T17:55:51-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 64526, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/20/59b07a6795e09/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Deadpool. In. Spaaaaace!!! Wade Wilson is heading off Earth on a personal mission - one that will land him in all manner of cosmic trouble! Plus, a secret story known only to compulsive Deadpool variant cover collectors, as Odin ejects Deadpool from reality -and into the cover-verse! Can a team-up with UPC-PO, the living embodiment of the UPC code, help Wade return to the world he left behind...or will it just be an excuse for parodies and shenanigans? We're guessing the latter. Collects Deadpool (2015) #30, Deadpool Secret Comic Variants."},
