  {title: "Fantastic Four/Inhumans (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-05-22T16:51:07-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 15916, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/03/4c7d620348245/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The incredible Inhumans have long been allies to the FF in defending the Earth, but what happens when they leave it? And what awaits them when they come back? See for yourself in a saga where treachery, intrigue and buried secrets reach from the depths of space to deep within Inhuman history! Guest-starring Ronan and Starlord of ANNIHILATION! Collecting INHUMANS (2000) #1-4 and FANTASTIC FOUR #51-54.\r<br>192 PGS./Rated T+ ...$19.99\r<br>ISBN: 0-7851-2703-8\r<br>"},
  {title: "Inhumans (2000) #2", modified: "2014-05-16T16:18:11-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 9323, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/30/53767236e26e9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #42", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 42, marvel_id: 7291, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/03/58641e52154b9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #43", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 43, marvel_id: 7292, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/70/5864272d0c1f6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Inhumans: Once and Future Kings (2017) #1", modified: "2017-08-04T17:33:33-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 63973, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/a0/59779631a5211/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SOMEDAY, ALL OF THIS WILL BE YOURS! A king in training. A brother destined for madness. These are the early days of the Boltagon legacy. When the king of the Inhumans is attacked, Black Bolt and Maximus spring into action to save their leader! But when Black Bolt loses control, what are the consequences for his future kingdom - or his own family? Plus: A two-page backup (in every issue!) starring Lockjaw, as told by UNBEATABLE SQUIRREL GIRL writer Ryan North and artist supreme Gustavo Duarte!"},
  {title: "4 (2004) #12", modified: "2016-12-02T13:53:40-0500", issue_number: 12, marvel_id: 52, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/e0/5841c31f01da8/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"THE STUFF OF DREAMS\" PART 3 (OF 3)\r\nEvery dream must come to an end-even the fear-induced nightmares that Psycho-Man is spreading across Manhattan!  It's the climax to the first year of Marvel Knights 4 and the final showdown between the FF and their reality-warping foe.  Hold onto your seats - especially you slight Marvelites - that wind blowing is a radical shift in the status quo of Marvel Comics' First Family of super heroes and adventurers!"},
  {title: "4 (2004) #19", modified: "2016-12-02T13:38:52-0500", issue_number: 19, marvel_id: 2120, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/e0/5841bfa08620b/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"Inhumane\" Part 1 (of 2)\r<br>The Inhumans live by their own rites and rituals, their own laws and governances. But when two Inhuman children seek asylum with the Fantastic Four, battle lines are drawn and an inter-species war threatens to erupt!  Old alliances are threatened and friends stand now as enemies!\r<br>32 PGS./T+ Suggested for Teens and Up ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "4 (2004) #20", modified: "2016-12-02T13:54:57-0500", issue_number: 20, marvel_id: 2230, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/d0/5841c36ddba30/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "INHUMANE\r<br>The conflict between the Family Fantastic and the Inhumans heats up with Black Bolt and Medusa's arrival on Earth. Sue is determined to keep the two Inhuman runaways safe no matter the cost, but with the rest of the FF wondering if they should even be involved in this dispute, what possible hope do she and the alien children have?   Part 2 [of 2]\r<br>32 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "4 (2004) #22", modified: "2016-12-02T13:54:19-0500", issue_number: 22, marvel_id: 2481, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/60/5841c34bbc8e5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"THE YANCY STREET GOLEM\"\r<br>\r<br>On Yancy Street, on the Lower East Side of Manhattan, someone--or something--is putting the hurt on the neighborhood's tough guys. Someone or something very large and very brutal, which is leaving a trail of twisted, broken bodies in its wake. Ben Urich, Jessica Jones, and the FF's ever-loving blue-eyed Thing are on the case, but what exactly is the nature of the threat they're facing?  \r<br>\r<br>\r<br>32 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "4 Vol. 2: The Stuff of Nightmares (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2016-12-02T13:53:40-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 1550, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/50/4bc6570d18f3c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "While New York freezes in the icy grip of winter, an old foe resurfaces with a grudge: Namor! And the crown prince is demanding Sue make good on an old promise - even if it's over Reed's dead body. Meanwhile, closer to home, Johnny may be the only person who can help a Washington Heights woman find her missing son. Plus: Something very, very strange is happening to New York's First Family of Super Heroes. Their deepest fears and doubts are spreading from their dreams - their unconscious minds - to the waking world. What's real and what's not? The FF's old villain Psycho-Man may hold the key, but he's...dying?! Collects MARVEL KNIGHTS 4 #8-12."},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #653", modified: "2014-05-01T12:49:52-0400", issue_number: 653, marvel_id: 32217, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/f0/4e9833f4aee81/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "REVENGE OF THE SPIDER-SLAYER PART 2 No one in Spidey's life is safe-from the offices of the Daily Bugle to the Mayor's staff at City Hall! It's way more than our wall-crawler can handle. Guest-starring The New Avengers!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #654", modified: "2014-05-01T12:49:58-0400", issue_number: 654, marvel_id: 35521, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/70/5809216996f27/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "REVENGE OF THE SPIDER-SLAYER PART 3 The final showdown between Alistair Smythe and Spidey is here!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #654 (2nd Printing Variant)", modified: "2011-03-22T01:30:34-0400", issue_number: 654, marvel_id: 39595, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/d0/4e983c691d9f9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "REVENGE OF THE SPIDER-SLAYER Part 3 of 3\n\"Self-Inflicted Wounds\"\nOne of the most pivotal moments of the SPIDER-MAN \"BIG TIME\" era happens here.  Other comics promise you their issues will \"Change Everything\" or that \"Nothing Will Ever Be The Same.\"  No carnival barker-like pitch this time.  Just the plain, simple truth: This issue of AMAZING SPIDER-MAN will have repercussions for Peter Parker and this title's cast for years and years to come. Guest-starring THE NEW AVENGERS.  Also in this issue: We finally reveal what has become of the alien symbiote.  And a dramatic change to Spider-Man's powers. Do NOT miss this issue!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #657", modified: "2014-05-01T12:50:07-0400", issue_number: 657, marvel_id: 35497, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/30/4d87a9336fa68/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "FF: THREE TIE-IN Spider-Man visits the FF for a very private wake-just for family."},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #658", modified: "2014-05-01T12:50:10-0400", issue_number: 658, marvel_id: 39019, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/03/580a359142c92/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Johnny Storm has fallen. Who shall take his place? Why, it's your Friendly Neighborhood Spider-Man! Prepare for the Future Foundation's first mission with the Wallcrawler on the team roster!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #658 (THOR HOLLYWOOD VARIANT)", modified: "2011-04-07T15:52:03-0400", issue_number: 658, marvel_id: 38716, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/70/4e9f1bd557510/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "CLASSIFIED!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #659", modified: "2014-05-01T12:50:12-0400", issue_number: 659, marvel_id: 39018, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/03/580a42069e692/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "To the end of the universe! To the future and back! Up and down the Microverse! And France! These are the varied destinations on the FF's itinerary. Can Spidey handle the harrowing, universe-spanning antics of the FF?"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #659 (2nd Printing Variant)", modified: "2011-06-03T11:04:15-0400", issue_number: 659, marvel_id: 40882, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/60/4e9f22c54bcd4/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Spider-Man joins the Future Foundation for a fantastic new adventure!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #660", modified: "2014-05-01T12:50:15-0400", issue_number: 660, marvel_id: 35505, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/10/4e9f2554926c4/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "It's the Sinister Six versus The Future Foundation! But what happens when the world's deadliest super-villains take on the entire FF, including the kids?"},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #3", modified: "2013-04-09T16:28:31-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 29206, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/a0/5a26b9a64288c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Avengers must travel to the far flung future to see the mess their children have made of the world. But what if Kang didn't tell our heroes the truth about what has gone wrong. Guest starring the Next Avengers and the Future Imperfect Hulk!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #663", modified: "2014-05-01T12:50:27-0400", issue_number: 663, marvel_id: 35501, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/50/580e212952c6d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"The Ghost of Jean DeWolff\" ANTI-VENOM returns to help SPIDER-MAN wage war against MISTER NEGATIVE and his criminal empire... whether Spidey wants him to or not. And when an all-new WRAITH enters the fray, will she prove to be a friend or foe?  Plus: From the pages of SECRET AVENGERS, a special guest appearance by SHANG-CHI, The Master of Kung Fu! PLUS: \"Infested\" continues in...the lead-in to SPIDER-ISLAND."},
  {title: "1602 (2003) #4", modified: "2013-07-30T10:52:58-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 148, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/40/4d24f4a04b398/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "With the country in turmoil, Dr. Strange learns Virginia Dare's dark secret, Peter Parquargh is captured by the X-Men, and Fury is placed in an impossible position! 32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$3.50"},
  {title: "4 (2004) #17", modified: "2016-12-02T13:54:37-0500", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 1875, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/90/5841c3593e6d0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"DIVINE TIME\" \r<br>In the far past, in a reality that shouldn't exist, the fight for the future rages on! Branded as outlaws and trapped in a pyramid of horrors-with no modern technology at their disposal-how will Reed, Sue, and Ben escape Ancient Egypt to stop the mad tyrant Ramades in the present? And where exactly is Johnny? Cut off from his teammates, can it be that his only hope for survival is...DOOM? \r<br>Part 3 (of 4)\r<br>32 PGS./Marvel PSR ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "4 Vol. 3: Divine Time (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2016-12-02T13:54:37-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 2189, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/00/4bc654a09a5be/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "In New York, it's springtime - and business as usual for the FF, as they celebrate Franklin's team making it to the Little League playoffs. But around the globe, the very fabric of time is unraveling. Minutes are vanishing from days, and objects from the past are materializing in the present. When these chronal anomalies start multiplying like a virus, Reed, Sue, Ben and Johnny decide to slip into the timestream to investigate. For seasoned adventurers like the FF, it should be a walk in the park, right? Guess again. Plus: It's good news all around - and not just for the FF, who have reclaimed their status as New York's premier super-hero team, but for their friend and ally, Alicia Masters. After a lifetime of darkness, the blind sculptress's eyesight has been restored by her father, Philip Masters - the seemingly reformed villain Puppet Master - but at what cost? Either all is as it seems...or darker forces are at work. Collects MARVEL KNIGHTS 4 #13-18.\r\n144 PGS./T  SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$14.99"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1963) #5", modified: "2016-02-26T15:18:43-0500", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 6868, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/5192af9cf240c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Everyone's favorite neighborhood Spider-Man engages the Fantastic Four's most powerful enemy, Doctor Doom!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #15", modified: "2015-07-22T09:52:17-0400", issue_number: 15, marvel_id: 48430, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/80/57e91f6ecff84/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #16", modified: "2015-07-22T09:52:45-0400", issue_number: 16, marvel_id: 48431, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/e0/57e92699cf39d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1963) #350", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 350, marvel_id: 6761, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/b0/5201442d8a28a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Vengeance (2011) #6", modified: "2013-06-13T17:05:30-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 38991, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/90/51966fe04a5bf/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The newest ruler of Latveria is targeted for death by the Young Masters! Can the Teen Brigade rescue young Kristoff, before his assassination sparks a World War?"},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #6", modified: "2013-04-09T16:28:53-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 29209, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/10/5a26c0a481c8f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "It's Kang versus Ultron with Avengers from every era right in the middle!"},
  {title: "Avengers (1996) #12", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 12, marvel_id: 17754, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/e0/58766a04db837/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1998) #56", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 56, marvel_id: 17541, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/f0/5863dbd42c777/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Elements of Doom run wild in St. Louis, and only the Avengers can stop them! But the menace of dozens of power-mad life-forms isn't the only gauntlet the Avengers must run - and it may not even be the worst!"},
  {title: "Avengers (1998) #63", modified: "2017-01-03T13:17:23-0500", issue_number: 63, marvel_id: 17549, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/60/586bcf99c97b0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "In Eastern Europe, Thor and the Asgardians seek justice - but they may bring war instead, at least if Doctor Doom has his way! Iron Man and Captain America must salvage what they can from a standoff that could shatter the Avengers with a thunder god's hammer!"},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #155", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 155, marvel_id: 7014, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/5880f1062dcdd/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #156", modified: "2011-10-12T16:04:20-0400", issue_number: 156, marvel_id: 7015, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/d0/4e95f30dcb739/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "A+X (2012) #10", modified: "2013-07-15T23:48:35-0400", issue_number: 10, marvel_id: 43509, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/70/584ffaa0e47fa/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "<ul><li>BLACK WIDOW and FANTOMEX find themselves on opposite sides of the law in Russia!</li><li>SCARLET WITCH and DOMINO try their luck together!</li></ul>"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #4", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 7415, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/e0/4bb589d21c02c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #6", modified: "2012-11-26T18:28:57-0500", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 7437, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/20/50b3fb0e48941/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #7", modified: "2012-11-26T18:26:25-0500", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 7448, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/30/50b3fa751c674/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #8", modified: "2012-11-27T15:28:14-0500", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 7459, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/c0/50b522286e321/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #13", modified: "2010-11-12T12:54:54-0500", issue_number: 13, marvel_id: 23971, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/4ea19c8c0760d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MESSIAH WAR PART 2 Cable has travelled forward in the time stream to keep the so-called mutant messiah safe from the clutches of Lucas Bishop. In an effort to rescue to the time-travelling pair, Cyclops dispatches X-force!"},
  {title: "A-Force (2016) #9", modified: "2016-09-02T10:57:45-0400", issue_number: 9, marvel_id: 56020, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/a0/57c0acaf956ef/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "CIVIL WAR II TIE-IN! The fates of NICO MINORU, a mysterious missing girl named Alice, and a small town in Colorado are all tied together as CIVIL WAR II heats up and threatens to tear A-FORCE apart. The team, with ELSA BLOODSTONE in foul-mouthed tow, splits up to hunt down the apparent source of the trouble in the hopes of saving the town. However, it soon becomes apparent that all is not what it seems with the team—A-Force is changing—and by morning there may not be anyone left to save the day."},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #13 (OLIVETTI (MW, 50/50 COVER))", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 13, marvel_id: 23972, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/e0/4ea19f9b18942/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"X-FORCE/CABLE: MESSIAH WAR,\" PART 2 \r\nThe sequel to 2007's MESSIAH COMPLEX continues here!  Cyclops has complete faith that his son, Cable, will do everything he can to protect the so-called mutant messiah - who he believes will save mutantkind. But he also knows what havoc former X-Man Lucas Bishop has wreaked in the nightmarish future.  So now he's sent his black ops team, the X-Force, on a risky, time-traveling mission to save Cable and the child, completely unaware that there's something else waiting for them in the future.  Something not even Bishop was counting on...\r\nRated T  ...$2.99"},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #14", modified: "2010-11-12T13:47:20-0500", issue_number: 14, marvel_id: 24171, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/20/4ea1b32b48e75/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MESSIAH WAR PART 4 As X-Force struggles to escape from a deadly trap, Cable must find the mutant messiah before it is too late!"},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #14 (OLIVETTI MW, 50/50 COVER)", modified: "2014-05-07T14:24:25-0400", issue_number: 14, marvel_id: 24172, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/40/4ea1b72ade030/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"X-FORCE/CABLE: MESSIAH WAR,\" PART 4 \r\nThe sequel to 2007's MESSIAH COMPLEX continues here!  \"Messiah War,\" the much-anticipated sequel to \"Messiah\r\nCompleX,\" continues here! For the first time, Cable's been separated from the girl he's sworn to raise and protect - Hope, the so-called \"Mutant Messiah\" - and now she's in the hands of his greatest enemy!  Meanwhile, X-Force, sent by Cyclops on a desperate rescue mission to the deep future, scrambles to find their way out of a trap that will kill them in matter of hours.  And if that's not enough, an old - some might say ancient - enemy of the X-Men has reared his ugly head one last time...\r\nRated T  ...$2.99"},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #15", modified: "2010-11-12T13:54:59-0500", issue_number: 15, marvel_id: 24631, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/f0/4ea1ba4b5cb88/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MESSIAH WAR PART 6 Cable faces a threat at every corner. Two of his deadliest enemies are hunting him through the time stream, X-Force has come to take Cable back to the present, and Hope is beginning to doubt her protector's abilities."},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #15", modified: "2017-06-21T16:38:47-0400", issue_number: 15, marvel_id: 7388, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/10/594c3c4445c10/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "He's clashed with Stryfe, he's tangled with Omega Red, and he's survived some of the most hellish battles you can possibly imagine. But is Cable ready for the ultimate challenge…a date with Domino?"},
  {title: "Cable (2008) #15 (OLIVETTI (MW, 50/50 COVER))", modified: "2011-10-21T14:53:52-0400", issue_number: 15, marvel_id: 24632, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/20/4ea1bf52c8a74/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"MESSIAH WAR, PART 6\"\r\nOne thousand years from now, Cable is having a very, very bad day.  His own father doubts his ability to protect the mutant messiah.  His former team, X-Force, has shown up to bring him back to the present, whether he likes it or not.  Not one, but two of Cable's oldest and deadliest enemies threaten to annihilate them all.  And now even Hope, the mutant messiah he's raised since birth, is starting to wonder if Cable's the right man for the job of keeping her alive...The penultimate chapter of \"Messiah War\" -- the sequel to the groundbreaking, game-changing \"Messiah Complex\" -- is here!\r\nRated T  ...$2.99"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #17", modified: "2017-06-21T16:41:28-0400", issue_number: 17, marvel_id: 7390, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/e0/594c3c3510b6a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE DARK RIDE begins here! Cable and Domino visit the X-Men, but reunions are cut short by the appearance of the Dark Riders! What are the Riders after, and who is behind their resurgence?"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #18", modified: "2017-06-21T16:42:16-0400", issue_number: 18, marvel_id: 7391, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/80/56f956a8e771e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The chase of the Dark Riders is on! Cable, Domino and Storm are on the Riders' trail when they are suddenly transported to the scene of a massacre! Who is responsible for this horror, and how is Cable's son Tyler connected to it all?"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #23", modified: "2017-06-21T16:46:41-0400", issue_number: 23, marvel_id: 7397, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/00/56f958b801ded/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cable goes to Professor X with an important request - help Nathan track down his wayward son, Tyler Summers! Plus, a murder investigation brings Domino face to face with an old friend!"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #24", modified: "2017-06-21T16:47:30-0400", issue_number: 24, marvel_id: 7398, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/a0/56f95925d8d37/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Domino takes on Grizzly! But can she bring herself to fight a long-time friend? Then Cable makes a major decision - to return to his future timeline!"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #25", modified: "2017-06-21T16:48:12-0400", issue_number: 25, marvel_id: 7399, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/60/594d319662785/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cable and Domino head back to the future! It's a race against time as the two battle-hardened mutants fight to save the life of…Nathan Summers!?"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #26", modified: "2017-06-21T16:48:52-0400", issue_number: 26, marvel_id: 7400, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/10/56f959a7d610e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Finally returning from the future, Cable and Domino find themselves smack in then middle of an all-out war! What happened to cause such a savage conflict to flare up like this?"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #27", modified: "2017-06-21T16:49:37-0400", issue_number: 27, marvel_id: 7401, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/00/56f95a4b9fa6c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The truth behind the Genoshan civil war revealed! But can Cable, Domino and their unlikely allies bring an end to the fighting before it's too late!"},
  {title: "Annihilation (2006) #6", modified: "2016-03-29T16:23:11-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 5795, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/e0/57850eb63ba98/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Nova and Annihilus face off in a fight to the finish with the fates of two, count 'em, two, universes at stake.  You think that's bad?  Wait until you see what happens when Galactus decides to go to war."},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1998) #19", modified: "2013-08-05T11:43:15-0400", issue_number: 19, marvel_id: 15537, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/80/51ffc7e247108/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1998) #42", modified: "2013-08-19T14:51:30-0400", issue_number: 42, marvel_id: 15563, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/c0/52126edbb137c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1998) #43", modified: "2013-07-24T13:17:16-0400", issue_number: 43, marvel_id: 15564, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/00/51f00bf866a42/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1998) #44", modified: "2016-09-27T17:58:50-0400", issue_number: 44, marvel_id: 15565, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/80/51d1a31e5b524/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Negative Zone epic ends here!"},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1961) #256", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 256, marvel_id: 13068, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/20/4bb793fe88344/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #2", modified: "2014-05-12T12:47:49-0400", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 29205, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/b0/5a26b70b47aad/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Avengers have assembled! The villainous Kang has revealed that they must travel to the future to save their own children from destroying the universe. Find out who is the newest member to join the ranks of the Earth's Mightiest!"},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #3 (ROMITA JR. VARIANT)", modified: "2017-12-05T10:29:00-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 34142, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/00/4c4075bfc08ad/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The time space continuum is broken!  And the Avengers must travel to the far flung future to see exactly what terrible mess their children have made of the world. But maybe, just maybe, Kang didn't tell our heroes the truth about what has gone wrong.  Guest starring the Next Avengers, the Future Imperfect Hulk and the Amazing Spider-Girl!  Yeah, you heard us! Another blockbuster issue from Brian Michael Bendis and John Romita, Jr.!  Plus! Another chapter in the untold oral history of the Avengers by Brian Michael Bendis...!\r\nRated A ...$3.99"},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #35", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 35, marvel_id: 7410, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/4bb5881d5c4c2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #66", modified: "2018-01-05T16:44:38-0500", issue_number: 66, marvel_id: 7444, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/40/5a4fbb9163fd2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "It is the End of Times! Cable vs. Apocalypse, with the fate of humankind at stake."},
  {title: "Cable (1993) #75", modified: "2016-11-18T19:19:29-0500", issue_number: 75, marvel_id: 7454, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/d0/56f95d5827d78/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Apocalypse’s Horseman Wolverine takes on Cable!"},
  {title: "Extraordinary X-Men Vol. 3: Kingdoms Fall (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-02-10T15:06:35-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 55262, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/60/589e1c6fe73e6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "An ancient evil stirs in the periphery of Limbo, consuming mystical realms, and little does Magik suspect that the X-Men's newest charge is drawing it straight to X-Haven! Meanwhile, Colossus is rampaging across Earth...as a Horseman of Apocalypse. Can Nightcrawler and Iceman stop their longtime friend and teammate and wrest him from Apocalypse's grasp? COLLECTING: EXTRAORDINARY X-MEN (2016) #13-16, Annual."},
  {title: "Further Adventures of Cyclops & Phoenix (1996) #4", modified: "2017-06-15T15:36:56-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 60188, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/a0/5941ba4a91e9f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cyclops and Phoenix at last return to the present…or try to, that is! Standing in their way is the newly transformed Mr. Sinister, destined to become one of their greatest foes…if they can survive!"},
  {title: "Incredible Hulk (1962) #456", modified: "2010-11-02T19:05:20-0400", issue_number: 456, marvel_id: 9267, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/50/594ae3777c458/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Mystic Comics 70th Anniversary Special (2009) #1 (MARTIN VARIANT)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 26022, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/80/4bb3f0789c42e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"I am the destroyer of evil,\" the haunting stranger intoned; \"I've crossed the great cold into your world!\" So speaks the original Vision! From a dimension beyond, comes an otherworldly force of retribution. His steely touch turns killers to ice, shattering them. His staggering gaze drives the guilty mad with terror. His unstoppable power never fails to punish the wicked! It is said only those approaching death can see him in his true form as...the Vision!\r\nOne-Shot/New & Reprint/Rated A ...$3.99"},
  {title: "Official Handbook of the Marvel Universe (2004) #8", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 1489, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/80/4bc65a8e339db/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The House of Ideas celebrates 65 years with a timely return to the Golden Age of comics! OHOTMUGAM04 includes in-depth bios on more than 40 of Marvel's most venerable heroes - from Angel to Yellow Claw!"},
  {title: "Official Handbook of the Marvel Universe (2004) #9 (THE WOMEN OF MARVEL)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 9, marvel_id: 1590, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/b0/4c7d666c0e58a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Marvel's leading ladies take center stage! This Official Handbook includes in-depth bios on more than 40 of the House's most powerful women warriors - from Araña to Vindicator! Plus: an all-new cover by superstar artist Greg Land!"},
  {title: "Official Handbook of the Marvel Universe (2004) #10 (MARVEL KNIGHTS)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 10, marvel_id: 1689, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/30/4bc64df4105b9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "On the mean streets of the Marvel Universe, the kid gloves come off. Guardian devils, vengeance-seeking vigilantes and enigmatic assassins stalk the city's dark underbelly _ and the urban action unfolds with gritty intensity. The newest entry in Marvel's best-selling Handbook series, OHOTMUMK04 includes in-depth bios on a host of the House's edgiest icons - from Black Panther to Shang-Chi!"},
  {title: "Official Handbook of the Marvel Universe (2004) #11 (X-MEN - AGE OF APOCALYPSE)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 11, marvel_id: 1749, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/b0/4bc6494ed6eb4/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Your complete guide to the epic saga! This Official Handbook includes in-depth bios on more than 40 denizens of the Age of Apocalypse - from Abyss to Weapon X! Plus: An all-new cover by superstar-in-waiting Mark Brooks, digitally painted by Justin Ponsor.\r<br>48 PGS./Marvel PSR ...$3.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "A-Force (2016) #6", modified: "2016-05-23T17:00:03-0400", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 56017, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/10/573a21c38e9a0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The mysterious (and formerly looking like a Dragon!) Countess has taken over the town A-Force came to save, rebuilding it in her own image and with a mind-controlled NICO MINORU at her side. It’s A-FORCE vs NICO and the team (and one innocent town!) is learning the hard way just how powerful Nico can be. Will this be the end of A-Force at the hands of one of their own? Or will SHE-HULK’S risky (okay, sure, some say insane) plan, allow them to live long enough to fight another day?!"},
  {title: "A-Force (2016) #7", modified: "2016-07-12T16:41:25-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 56018, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/20/57855538e2f42/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "After narrowly escaping a grisly death at the hands of one of their own, a weary but determined A-FORCE make bold moves to free NICO and the town from Countess’s control. However, saving the day is going to take more than just super-powered punches. A-FORCE is going to have to go deeper than that – changing Countess’s very mind – which is not exactly something super villains readily embrace. Meanwhile, developments with the team’s sparkly THOR rock A-FORCE to the core."},
  {title: "A-Force (2016) #8", modified: "2016-08-12T14:19:12-0400", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 56019, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/50/57a359f4aafd0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "CIVIL WAR II TIE-IN! Civil War has come to A-FORCE! As the team is wrecked by a personal tragedy things only get worse when a predictive vision proclaims one of A-FORCE is a murderer. CAPTAIN MARVEL attempts an arrest, creating a rift that may very well mean the end of the team, and setting in motion a chain of devastating events that affect far more than just A-FORCE. Meanwhile foul-mouthed, gun-toting ELSA BLOODSTONE just unofficially joined A-Force. Looks like we’re gonna need a bigger boat...and a verrrrry big black censor bar."},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #38", modified: "2015-11-04T14:48:06-0500", issue_number: 38, marvel_id: 7263, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/b0/5863dde41db7e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #39", modified: "2014-02-26T14:46:28-0500", issue_number: 39, marvel_id: 7274, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/f0/5863f569bb4f0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "A-Force (2016) #10", modified: "2016-10-12T15:26:00-0400", issue_number: 10, marvel_id: 56021, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/e0/57fe46e6e87e8/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "CIVIL WAR II TIE-IN!\nThe lives of A-FORCE, a mysterious woman named Alice and an entire town lie in the hands of NICO MINORU. What Nico chooses to do next can save the day but can also make her a murderer — the very thing she’s been running from since CAPTAIN MARVEL first tried to arrest her. And if A-Force manages to survive the day, can the team stay together? Or will this be the end of A-Force as we know it?"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1963) #62", modified: "2014-04-11T15:26:46-0400", issue_number: 62, marvel_id: 6882, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/30/57acc50571e2f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #9", modified: "2013-04-09T16:29:18-0400", issue_number: 9, marvel_id: 29212, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/40/5a26c8cf62180/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Joined by the Incredible Red Hulk, The Avengers fight The Hood as he fights to bring the Infinity Gauntlet together once more. Meanwhile, who is coming to Earth to try and claim the gauntlet?\n"},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #11", modified: "2013-04-09T16:29:33-0400", issue_number: 11, marvel_id: 29197, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/f0/5a26d734aa4f2/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Infinity Gauntlet is in the hands of the most dangerous human on the planet! The Avengers are the only force that can stand in his way!"},
  {title: "Avengers (2010) #11 (CAPTAIN AMERICA 70TH ANNIVERSARY VARIANT)", modified: "2017-12-05T12:38:42-0500", issue_number: 11, marvel_id: 38617, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/90/4d87ae2d03ff6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Infinity Gauntlet is in the hands of the most dangerous human being on the planet. But what can the Avengers do against a power greater than anything known on Earth? Another explosive chapter in this epic Avengers event by Bendis and Romita Jr. featuring the debut of a brand-new cosmic character that you won't want to miss!! Plus: another illustrated chapter of the oral history of the Avengers!"},
  {title: "Beyond! (Hardcover)", modified: "2016-03-07T10:28:03-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 6040, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/30/56dd98067e246/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "An indescribably powerful cosmic being gathers nine of Marvel's most mismatched super-beings for purposes beyond their comprehension. Can Spider-Man, Gravity, Venom, Henry Pym, the Wasp, Medusa, Kraven, Firebird and the Hood keep from killing each other before they must face the dangers of their destination, the deadly artificial planet known as Battleworld? Collecting BEYOND! #1-6.\r<br>144 PGS./Rated A ...$19.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Beyond! (2006) #1", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4447, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/60/56dd9dbc2e44a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "An indescribably powerful cosmic being gathers nine of Marvel's most mismatched super beings for purposes beyond their comprehension. Can Spider-Man, Gravity, Venom, Henry Pym, The Wasp, Medusa, Kraven, Firebird and the Hood keep from killing each other before they have to face the dangers of their destination, the deadly artificial planet known as Battleworld?\r<br>32 PGS./Rated A ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Civil War II (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-10-19T17:31:13-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 58678, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/03/59e923b028190/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "When a new Inhuman named Ulysses manifests uncanny precognitive powers, Earth’s protectors must wrestle with the consequences. And when one of Ulysses’ visions leads to tragedy, an old friendship reaches a breaking point — and longtime teammates Captain Marvel and Iron Man find themselves at odds. Is it right to act now on crimes yet to be committed? Do the ends justify the means? And how reliable is Ulysses’ gift? As Avengers, X-Men, Inhumans, Spider-Men, Guardians of the Galaxy and more stand divided between the two figureheads, the battle lines are drawn. And when one of the greatest among them falls, the Marvel Universe is once again set on a path to war — but will the fight for the future leave one worth saving? Collecting CIVIL WAR II #0-8 and material from FREE COMIC BOOK DAY 2016 (CIVIL WAR II) #1."},
  {title: "Civil War II: Gods of War (2016) #3", modified: "2016-08-08T16:05:29-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 59614, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/a0/57a8b8978a818/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MEET THE DEITIES READY TO SAVE THE DAY. As a civil war rips through the Marvel Universe, HERCULES battles to stop the Uprising Storm…the one threat no one else is aware of. But if the first super hero is going to save the world, he’s going to need help, and not even the Avengers are going to stand in his way. With no one else to turn to, Herc must recruit heroes of myth to stand at his side. HERE COME GILGAMESH, BEOWULF, IRE, THESEUS, SIGURD and LORELEI…the GODS OF WAR!"},
  {title: "Assault on New Olympus Prologue One-Shot (2009) #1", modified: "2010-11-02T18:09:30-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 29277, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/e0/56dddf0d976f0/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Hercules! Spider-Man! Ares! New Avengers! Wolverine! Mighty Avengers! The Agents of Atlas! If there's a bigger event this fall, we don't know what it could be! At long last, the Prince of Power takes the fight to his villainous stepmother Hera and the forces of the Olympus Group -- just as she unleashes the most terrifying threat the Marvel Universe has ever seen! But first Herc has to gather together a star-studded strike force from the ranks of the New and the Mighty Avengers! First on the list: THE AMAZING SPIDER-MAN! But why is Everyone's Friendly Neighborhood fighting against Hercules? Has he joined the side of the dark gods? It's webs and wisecracks versus Olympian power in this super-sized one-shot! (There will be major property damage, we guarantee.) Plus: The iHerc team proudly welcomes our new INCREDIBLE HERCULES on-going back-up feature... THE AGENTS OF ATLAS, written by fan favorite scribe Jeff Parker! When the forces of New Olympus target Venus, will Jimmy Woo lead his team into the fray for or against Hercules' forces?\r\nOne-Shot/Rated T  ...$3.99"},
  {title: "Avengers (2016) #1", modified: "2017-08-24T17:42:16-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 61373, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/20/580e547031c2f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The time has come! Their ranks shattered by Civil War, their spirits weighted down by a toll both personal and spiritual, Earth’s Mightiest Heroes must find the resolve to stand united one final time against their greatest foe! Captain America! Thor! The Vision! The Wasp! Spider-Man! Hercules! When the dust settles, not a one of these valiant heroes will make it to the final page alive! This is KANG WAR ONE!"},
  {title: "Avengers (2016) #8", modified: "2017-06-02T14:20:50-0400", issue_number: 8, marvel_id: 61380, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/c0/593061a9a0521/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Once and for all, the Avengers have to decide whether the Infamous Iron Man is friend or foe! It's hard to trust an \"ally\" you've been fighting against for years — but the Avengers will have to!"},
  {title: "Avengers (2016) #11", modified: "2017-09-13T14:02:01-0400", issue_number: 11, marvel_id: 61383, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/00/59b93d40222bc/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SECRET EMPIRE AFTERMATH! Not every Avenger came out of the Secret Empire's regime the same as going in. One of Earth's Mightiest, in particular, will either step up to lead the team - or retire altogether!"},
  {title: "Avengers (1998) #25", modified: "2014-01-23T11:05:03-0500", issue_number: 25, marvel_id: 17507, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/e0/58595d3b3ddfc/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Avengers interrupt Juggernaut's execution and battle the Exemplars. Plus: an Avenger takes a leave from the active roster!"},
  {title: "Avengers (1998) #44", modified: "2014-01-23T11:05:55-0500", issue_number: 44, marvel_id: 17528, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/80/58627e3380ab5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #44", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 44, marvel_id: 7293, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/70/586432b3997c9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Classic X-Men (1986) #20", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 20, marvel_id: 20575, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/a0/4bb682f9ad9a3/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
