  {title: "5 Ronin (2010) #5", modified: "2017-08-11T18:10:59-0400", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 36160, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/10/598e2b64ccbf9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Travel back to medieval Japan to see Deadpool as you've never seen him before. This is the fifth ronin. Prepare for a wayward samurai's battle that may end in oblivion!"},
  {title: "5 Ronin (2010) #5 (MCGUINNESS COVER)", modified: "2011-03-25T11:24:51-0400", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 38751, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/90/4d8773dfaccdb/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "5 Books, 5 Heroes-1 unforgettable story of heroes pushed to their limits.  It is 17th century Japan, a time and place of violent upheaval, wandering Ronin, and mysterious Geisha. Into this strange and dangerous world come Wolverine, Pyslocke, Punisher, Hulk and Deadpool. Five of Marvel's greatest heroes...as you've never seen them before. Each has been wronged by a powerful tyrant. Each has taken a solemn vow...of vengeance!\n5 Books, 5 Heroes, 5 Weeks...1 spell-binding story."},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #611", modified: "2015-12-03T10:28:35-0500", issue_number: 611, marvel_id: 24418, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/70/58078e371993e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Prepare for the Deadpool and Spider-Man team-up of the century! What has brought the Merc With A Mouth to Spidey's neck of the woods? What does it have to do with the arduous trials he will come to face in his future? Plus, Lady Stilt-Man!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #620 (DEADPOOL VARIANT)", modified: "2011-09-29T12:35:54-0400", issue_number: 620, marvel_id: 31556, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/20/4e849e9e406a5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "MYSTERIO'S made his big move and a criminal empire is his for the taking!  Or is that just more sleight of hand? More mobsters! More mayhem! More magic tricks!  And a fight to the finish with MR. NEGATIVE versus SPIDER-MAN versus MYSTERIO! The big question is: What prize goes to the winner?\r\nRated A"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man Annual (2011) #38", modified: "2011-04-04T09:00:13-0400", issue_number: 38, marvel_id: 36956, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/20/56d7257674c5d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"IDENTITY WARS,\" A THREE-PART ANNUAL EVENT STARTS HERE!\n\nIn a perfect world, what could possibly go wrong?\n\nAn exciting new story by Eisner Award Winning writers JOHN LAYMAN (Chew) and LEE GARBETT (Batgirl).\n\nPeter Parker thinks life couldn't get any better-until an explosion at Horizon Labs plummets him (along with Deadpool and Hulk) into another dimension where The Amazing-Spider is the world's most powerful and beloved hero and Peter Parker is a billionaire mogul playboy (with surprises in his supporting cast). Will Peter discover the price for perfection? And what dreams come true does this dimension hold for Deadpool and Hulk?  Find out as the story continues in their respective Annuals in May and June."},
  {title: "Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #33 (DEADPOOL VARIANT)", modified: "2011-10-12T14:58:45-0400", issue_number: 33, marvel_id: 31560, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/60/4e95e392e302a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Initiative faces its own CIVIL WAR as\r\nTaskmaster, Constrictor and Diamondback join the Dark Avengers in the Siege of Asgard...and come face-to-hammer with Thor! Meanwhile, Justice, Tigra and the rest of the Avengers Resistance assault camp H.A.M.M.E.R., aiming to bring it down once and for all - but the Hood is ready for them! It's all-out war on two fronts\r\n- and one side won't be here when it's over!\r\nRated T"},
  {title: "Baby's First Deadpool Book (1998) #1", modified: "2016-10-07T13:48:33-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 45720, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/70/57d7fba481dad/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Three stories starring Deadpool! The Merc with a Mouth goes to the aquarium with Blind Al, learns to be a Good Samaritan with Captain America, and crashes a birthday party (literally) with Blarney the dinosaur!"},
  {title: "Battle Scars (2011) #3", modified: "2013-04-02T15:23:24-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 41349, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/03/515b3495b4367/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Deadpool joins the hunt for Marcus Johnson while the greatest secret in the Marvel Universe begins to unravel. Plus, Taskmaster knows more than he's saying...and Marcus Johnson wants answers!"},
  {title: "Battle Scars (2011) #4", modified: "2012-01-27T13:56:26-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 41348, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/20/51e4003082311/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Marcus faces off against Taskmaster, Deadpool and the Serpent Society! And, the villain that made Marcus the most wanted man in the Marvel Universe is revealed."},
  {title: "Black Panther (1998) #23", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 23, marvel_id: 12590, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/56ddeb1302f58/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #666", modified: "2014-12-29T10:03:41-0500", issue_number: 666, marvel_id: 35513, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/e0/57eaa30fd170e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE SPIDER-MAN STORY OF THE DECADE BEGINS WITH THS \"SPIDER-ISLAND: PRELUDE\"! Super-star writer Dan Slott and fan-favorite Spidey artist Stefano Caselli are back! New York has been INFESTED and the web grows as it gets ready to explode into SPIDER-ISLAND!  Normal people are getting Spider-Powers!  But not all of them realize that with great power must also come ....you know the rest. Okay, sure we often say Peter Parker's life will never be the same. But listen, pal, we've never been more serious. Heroes and villains are crawling all over Manahttan and no one knows why. This will change everything for Pete, for Spidey...and possibly for YOU! Look at it this way...If EVERYONE'S a Spider-Man then no one is."},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #668", modified: "2014-12-29T10:03:41-0500", issue_number: 668, marvel_id: 35532, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/10/57eac7c20aec6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "SPIDER-ISLAND PART TWO Spider-powered New York citizens! Spider-powered criminals! And Peter Parker fighting alongside Manhattan biggest super heroes-as Peter Parker?"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man: Worldwide Vol. 3 (Hardcover)", modified: "2018-02-01T17:06:49-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 66085, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/b0/5a7399ae5d135/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Death is no more, and the Clone Conspiracy rocks the Amazing Spider-Man’s world! And if things weren’t bad enough for the wall-crawler, Doctor Octopus has returned from the grave! What does Doc Ock have to do with the Jackal? Meanwhile, the return of Carrion means big trouble for the Scarlet Spider! Where has Kaine been, and what role will he play in the Jackal’s twisted plan? And while we’re asking questions, what could bring a resurrected Gwen Stacy to the villain’s side? When the Conspiracy ends, Norman Osborn is waiting on the other side! But even with a surprising old friend by his side, can Spider-Man battle an entire Goblin Army? Plus: Globe-trotting adventures starring Spidey in Mexico City, and Cloak and Dagger in Shanghai! Collecting AMAZING SPIDER-MAN (2015) #20-28 and ANNUAL (2016) #1."},
  {title: "Civil War (2006) #1", modified: "2015-04-28T12:11:29-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4216, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/f0/511307b2f1200/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE LANDSCAPE OF THE MARVEL U IS CHANGING AND IT'S TIME TO DECIDE: WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON? A conflict has been brewing in the Marvel Universe, threatening to pit friend against friend, brother against brother--and all it will take is a single misstep to cost thousands their lives and ignite the fuse!  As the war claims its first victims, no one is safe as teams, friendships, and families begin to fall apart. Starring Spider-Man, the New Avengers, the Fantastic Four, the X-Men and the entirety of the Marvel pantheon!"},
  {title: "Civil War (2006) #1 (Turner Variant)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4217, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/40/4bc5e6c93a70c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "THE LANDSCAPE OF THE MARVEL U IS CHANGING AND IT'S TIME TO DECIDE: WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON?  \r\nA conflict has been brewing in the Marvel Universe for over a year, threatening to pit friend against friend, brother against brother--and all it will take is a single misstep to cost thousands their lives and ignite the fuse!  As the war claims its first victims, no one is safe as teams, friendships, and families begin to fall apart.  Civil War, a Marvel Comics event in seven parts, stars Spider-Man, the New Avengers, the Fantastic Four, the X-Men and the entirety of the Marvel pantheon!  Civil War - the cross-over that rewrites the rules - begins here in this double-sized first issue!\r\n48 PGS./Rated T  ...$3.99"},
  {title: "Civil War (2006) #1 (sketch variant)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 4514, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/50/4bc5d5f4ac3f6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Go behind the lines of the Marvel Comics event starring Spider-Man, the New Avengers, the Fantastic Four, the X-Men and the entirety of the Marvel pantheon. This bonus edition reprints CIVIL WAR #1 - plus script, sketches, deleted scenes and more!\r\n64 PGS./ Rated T  ...$4.99"},
  {title: "Civil War (2006) #6", modified: "2013-02-06T20:55:28-0500", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 5227, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/e0/51130945d1273/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Captain America's depleted forces have determined the secret of File 42, setting them on a last-ditch collision course with Iron Man and the Pro-Registration heroes! It's the beginning f the battle of the century-a conflict in which virtually every superhuman on Earth will be forced to choose a side to fight on!"},
  {title: "Civil War (2006) #6 (Turner Variant)", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 5229, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/10/4bc5c3289ba15/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Captain America's depleted forces have determined the secret of File 42, setting them on a last-ditch collision \r<br>course with Iron Man and the Pro-Registration heroes! It's the beginning of the battle of the century-a conflict \r<br>in which virtually every superhuman on Earth will be forced to choose a side to fight on!\r<br>32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Spider-Island: Cloak & Dagger (2011) #3", modified: "2014-12-29T10:03:42-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 38986, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/d0/56b37d564a872/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Mr. Negative has created a monster...and the ultimate destiny of Cloak & Dagger is warped beyond recognition! Will Ty and Tandy live through the ordeal...and even if they do, can they ever be together again?!"},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1983) #1", modified: "2017-08-16T15:44:37-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 24117, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/c0/59fa1a79bcde6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cloak and Dagger, who wield the powers of darkness and light, set out to fight crime in New York City. But when a stray bullet from a street battle gone wrong harms a civilian, the superhuman duo may be forced to question their vigilante methodology..."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (2010) #1", modified: "2016-04-07T14:49:01-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 30053, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/40/5706ab8dd7896/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Marvel's most-requested duo return in this all-new one-shot, spinning out of X-MEN: NATION X! Cloak -- dark, brooding\r\nteleporter. Dagger -- deadly, shining mistress of light. Having quit the Dark X-Men, Cloak and Dagger find their partnership strained as they struggle to fit in among the mutants of Utopia. But when a new menace targets Cloak, Dagger must make a fateful choice for both of them. Guest-starring the X-Men, and written by Stuart Moore (WOLVERINE NOIR) with stunning art by Mark Brooks (YOUNG AVENGERS).\r\nOne-Shot/Rated T  ...$3.99"},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #1", modified: "2017-08-11T17:24:54-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 62782, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/5/20/58b89546d799e/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Learn the history of Cloak and Dagger! In their first issue, the duo takes down a human trafficking ring at a pornography shop. And Dagger visits her birth mother!"},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #2", modified: "2017-03-02T17:05:09-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 62783, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/80/58b893fc21044/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Dagger decides to dig deep into her roots, but is dismayed by her mother’s attitude towards her hard-edged life."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1983) #2", modified: "2013-03-07T19:00:32-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 24118, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/f0/4dc80b673a3ad/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cloak and Dagger's war on drugs and crime is in full swing. But are the police keen on letting the heroes of darkness and light continue to battle crime with their unorthodox methods? Plus, Cloak's hunger grows-what can sustain him now?"},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #3", modified: "2017-03-02T17:05:48-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 62784, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/50/58b8940f7d3f6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Guest-starring the Amazing Spider-Man! With the help of the Friendly Neighborhood crime fighter, Cloak and Dagger take down a crew of drug traffickers."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1983) #3", modified: "2011-06-24T14:11:17-0400", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 24119, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/e0/4dc8124ed9791/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cloak's dark hunger has grown to insurmountable levels. There is only one way to stop his need to consume, and that is for Dagger to offer up her light. All of it."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #4", modified: "2017-03-02T17:06:28-0500", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 62785, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/90/58b894249d746/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cloak and Dagger have their first encounter with The Beyonder, who, as usual wreaks havoc among their lives."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1983) #4", modified: "2012-04-03T18:05:56-0400", issue_number: 4, marvel_id: 24120, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/b0/4dc8135f4527f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Find out who Cloak and Dagger really are and how they came to be! Prepare for the origin of Marvel's mysterious crimefighting duo."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #5", modified: "2017-03-02T17:06:56-0500", issue_number: 5, marvel_id: 62786, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/1/70/58b89571455e6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Cloak and Dagger unknowingly help create a superhuman who is not only extraordinarily powerful, but very vengeful. Introducing Mayhem!"},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #6", modified: "2017-03-02T17:07:33-0500", issue_number: 6, marvel_id: 62787, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/c/03/58b895604c702/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "With Mayhem’s assist, Cloak and Dagger prevent a heroin ring from infiltrating the city."},
  {title: "Cloak and Dagger (1985) #7", modified: "2017-03-02T17:08:10-0500", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 62788, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/03/58b89532805b5/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Tandy and Tyrone are off to France! The super powered duo takes their war on drugs cross continental…and meet a new ally!"},
  {title: "Black Panther Annual (2008) #1", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 20715, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/597b8caa60d23/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"BLACK TO THE FUTURE\": A special double-sized issue to commemorate Black History Month.\r<br>It's 2057 and the Watcher's prediction came true: Wakanda is an Imperial Power steering the course for humanity's future.  As T'Challa prepares the next Black Panther for the great responsibility ahead, he must first reflect on the road traveled-a long and winding journey filled with surprises.\r<br>Rated T+...$3.99\r<br>"},
  {title: "Captain America Corps (2010) #1", modified: "2011-12-23T12:57:09-0500", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 36952, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/f0/4d88c8dea1ee6/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "A mysterious cosmic entity has recruited The U.S. Agent, American Dream, Commander A, Captain America, and...Captain America?! But what threat is so grave that two Captain Americas are needed? Who will lead the team?"},
  {title: "Captain Marvel (1968) #36", modified: "2017-12-14T12:19:15-0500", issue_number: 36, marvel_id: 8025, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/b0/5a306eff09f65/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Captain Marvel is back on Earth! Why has he returned?"},
  {title: "Captain Marvel (1968) #38", modified: "2017-12-14T12:24:39-0500", issue_number: 38, marvel_id: 8027, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/e/80/5a306ec1ccae3/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Trial of the Watcher!\n"},
  {title: "Captain Marvel (1968) #39", modified: "2017-12-14T12:26:17-0500", issue_number: 39, marvel_id: 8028, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/60/5a3071428f6df/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Mar-Vell and Rick finally come across the Temple of Justice!"},
  {title: "Deadpool (1997) #11", modified: "2015-12-03T10:24:24-0500", issue_number: 11, marvel_id: 8464, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/03/51b76248d8180/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Deadpool (1997) #24", modified: "2013-06-05T11:24:30-0400", issue_number: 24, marvel_id: 8478, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/a/00/4f20378fcb9f7/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Tiamat goes on a killing spree as a wounded Deadpool regroups and regenerates.\n"},
  {title: "Deadpool Team-Up (2009) #884", modified: "2012-10-10T11:45:44-0400", issue_number: 884, marvel_id: 36004, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/2/b0/564f4cc226010/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Deadpool's in trouble - he's stuck in an elevator with The Watcher! How will constantly being watched affect Deadpool's merc skills? And will the Watcher be able to keep his vow not to interfere in the affairs of men when Deadpool is really annoying?"},
  {title: "Deadpool Team-Up Vol. 3 (Hardcover)", modified: "2011-05-13T12:19:39-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 41028, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/7/20/4dcd59552765f/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Everyone's favorite Merc with a Mouth continues hacking and wisecracking his way across the Marvel Universe in this latest volume of riotous, ridiculous and outright reprehensible team-ups! In Round 1, it's clobberin' time as Deapoolmania runs wild on the Thing! In Round 2, Indiana Deadpool runs afoul of Thor amid Asgard's ruins and learns some treasures are best left undisturbed - particularly the ones containing evil, enormously powerful spirits imprisoned by Odin thousands of years hence. In Round 3, Deadpool and Iron Fist grudgingly team up to stop an ancient and villainous warlord - but Deadpool have to take down Iron Fist, as well, to secure his payday? In Round 4, gaze in horror upon the fiendish experiments inflicted upon Deadpool and Bessie the Vampire Cow by the malevolent Dr. Kilgore in the name of mad science, and bear witness to their terrible revenge! In Round 5, the voices in Deadpool's head hire him to do the dirtiest job of his career, but the mission is endangered when he's trapped in an elevator with the Watcher! In Round 6, Deadpool realizes there's no government bailout for super-powered mercenaries and is forced to do the unthinkable: look for a job! Luckily, Galactus has a position open in the Herald department. And for the knockout punch: Wolverine, Deadpool and a giant robot! Collecting DEADPOOL TEAM-UP #888-883 and WOLVERINE/DEADPOOL: THE DECOY (MDCU)."},
  {title: "Fantastic Four (1961) #13", modified: "2014-06-05T16:21:02-0400", issue_number: 13, marvel_id: 12928, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/b0/536d69249ea31/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "More than two hundred thousand miles from Earth, the Fantastic Four face the menace of The Red Ghost!"},
