  {title: "Black Widow (2010) #2", modified: "2013-11-04T14:58:17-0500", issue_number: 2, marvel_id: 29749, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/b0/5a2844bf44738/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Black Widow has narrowly escaped death. Recovering from her near-fatal injuries, Natasha sets out on a mission of retaliation! But what do Iron Man and Wolverine know about her attacker and why won't they help her? Find out here!"},
