  {title: "Daredevil (1998) #7", modified: "2011-06-24T14:14:36-0400", issue_number: 7, marvel_id: 15675, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/40/563271b9b470c/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The showdown between Daredevil and the man behind Karen's death, the appearance of the Messiah baby, and all that has befallen Matt Murdock is here! Two shall fight...one shall live."},
