  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #617", modified: "2014-04-18T11:11:33-0400", issue_number: 617, marvel_id: 24424, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/20/5807d04903ebb/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "The Gauntlet continues to close around Spider-Man in this heartbreaking story of love, loss and lust for power as the Rhino charges into Spider-Man's life, out to make a name for himself...by killing the Rhino?"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #625", modified: "2014-04-18T11:11:56-0400", issue_number: 625, marvel_id: 30300, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/50/5808dabe510d9/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "It's Rhino vs. Rhino - with Spidey caught in the middle! When the young, teched-out upstart who's taken the Rhino mantle refuses to leave the original Rhino, Aleski Systevich, in peace, he forces Systevich to make a stand..."},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man (1999) #644 (BACHALO VARIANT)", modified: "2011-09-20T10:47:03-0400", issue_number: 644, marvel_id: 36665, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/50/4e78a7e6bce96/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Part 3 of ORIGIN OF THE SPECIES.\nPlus the SPIDEY SUNDAY FEATURE continues!\nRated A $2.99"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man Family (2008) #3", modified: "-0001-11-30T00:00:00-0500", issue_number: 3, marvel_id: 22979, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/b/03/56d7169314e16/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "In our Untold Tales of Spider-Man, J.M. DeMatteis is back to take us through more of Peter Parker's struggle to become a hero.  In \"The Punch,\"  Pete struggles to keep his powers in check around Flash Thompson - and  discovers the negative examples a hero can set. Then, on a trip even further back in time, Matt Yocum takes us on an adventure of epic proportions with Pete's parents, Richard and Mary Parker - international parents of mystery!  Over in Mr. and Mrs. Spider-Man, during a late night hospital visit for baby May, Pete and MJ run into the Rhino - and discover even a super villain has a family.  Finally in our Told Tales of\r\nSpider-Man, take a look back at the demise of Harry Osborn in Spectacular Spider-Man #200!\r\nRated A ...$4.99"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man: Renew Your Vows (2016) #13", modified: "2017-11-17T09:20:13-0500", issue_number: 13, marvel_id: 61362, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/40/5a0c69764a2dc/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "EIGHT YEARS LATER Part 1. Jump eight years into the future with the web-slinging and wall-crawling Spider-Man family! Peter Parker and Mary Jane’s super-powered daughter, Annie, is now in high school. But when this teen isn’t in class, she’s swinging through the streets with her parents. After all, keeping New York safe from super villains is a family affair! But what new threat has emerged to menace the wall-crawlers? PLUS: Includes 3 bonus MARVEL PRIMER PAGES!"},
  {title: "Amazing Spider-Man: The Clone Conspiracy (Hardcover)", modified: "2017-04-08T09:18:53-0400", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 60236, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/f/f0/58e7e9eba2c9a/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Amidst a gauntlet of his deadliest rogues, an old foe returns to the fore. Loved ones lost are dead no more as Peter Parker plunges headlong into THE CLONE CONSPIRACY - a blockbuster event series from A-List creators Dan Slott and Jim Cheung! Prepare yourself for THE Spidey story of 2016 as the writer who brought you Spider-Verse, Superior Spider-Man and Spider-Island brings you the next defining chapter in the wallcrawler's life! The identity of the man in the red suit has been revealed. The Jackal has returned, more driven and determined than ever. He's off ered Spidey's greatest rogues a chance to reunite with their loved ones in exchange for loyalty. But to what end? With the Rhino, the Lizard, Electro and even Doctor Octopus at his side, things are looking bleak. But who else from Spider-Man's past has reappeared?! Collects Amazing Spider-Man (2015) #19-24; The Clone Conspiracy #1-5; The Clone Conspiracy: Omega; Silk (2015B) #14-17; Prowler (2016) 1-5; material from Free Comic Book Day 2016 (Captain America) #1."},
  {title: "Avengers (1963) #237", modified: "2014-04-23T14:47:39-0400", issue_number: 237, marvel_id: 7105, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/00/5873e1dc1033d/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
  {title: "Avengers Origins: Luke Cage (2013) #1", modified: "2016-09-22T13:57:23-0400", issue_number: 1, marvel_id: 32682, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/20/5a1ee6a139e61/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "\"What makes someone a hero? An Avenger? Is it super-powers? An indomitable will? An innate sense of right and wrong? For Luke Cage its one terrible mistake that has haunted him his entire life. But can a lifetime of good deeds make up for his years spent on the other side of the law? And will that past ever let him go, or will it tear him to pieces? \""},
  {title: "Cable & Deadpool (2004) #37", modified: "2014-08-20T16:48:32-0400", issue_number: 37, marvel_id: 6030, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/6/30/56e2cf09050f3/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "UNFINISHED BUSINESS PART 2 The last time these two faced off, Deadpool turned Rhino into a keychain. What happens when Deadpool tracks down Spidey's favorite rawhide in order to make amends for past misdeeds?"},
  {title: "Cable & Deadpool Vol. 7: Separation Anxiety (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2016-03-11T11:05:55-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 16217, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/8/a0/4bc5a3a56b045/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "Deadpool has decided to face the skeletons in his closet, dive deep into that dark void he calls a soul and rattle things up a bit.  First order of business: Taskmaster. Second order of business: a knock-down drag-out BRAWL! Plus: The aftermath of the X-Men's battle against the Hecatomb has cost Cable a huge chunk of his island paradise of Providence and an even bigger slice of his soul. With all his hopes for the future of the planet Earth in jeopardy, now would be a pretty bad time for a reunion with Deadpool, wouldn't it? And an even worse time for... an assassination! Collecting CABLE & DEADPOOL #36-42.\r<br>176 PGS./Rated T+ ...$17.99 \r<br>"},
  {title: "Captain America (1968) #413", modified: "2014-01-02T14:15:58-0500", issue_number: 413, marvel_id: 7794, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/d/00/59bff97b0cb75/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: nil},
