  {title: "All-New, All-Different Avengers (2015) #12", modified: "2016-07-21T15:16:49-0400", issue_number: 12, marvel_id: 55365, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/4/03/57911f1745d10/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "In chains, held captive millions of light-years from home, the Avengers are without salvation and without hope — unless they’re willing to make some hard choices. Plus: More on the new Wasp!"},
