  {title: "Decimation: X-Men the Day After (Trade Paperback)", modified: "2017-02-24T14:12:53-0500", issue_number: 0, marvel_id: 4072, image_path: "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/3/b0/4bc6175373f29/portrait_uncanny.jpg", description: "It was the worst day in X-Men history. Now it's the day after. The House of M is over, but the effects will be felt for the rest of their lives. How do the X-Men pick up the pieces in a world that has completely changed? Plus: Something's amiss at the House of Xavier! A sneak attack forces the X-Men to re-evaluate just who their friends are, and to align themselves with former enemies!\r<br>Collects DECIMATION: HOUSE OF M - THE DAY AFTER and X-MEN #177-181\r<br>168 PGS./Rated T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$17.99\r<br>"},
